%20Minister%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20drafting%20the%20now-scrapped%20policy%20and%20seeking%20bribes%2C%20or%20kickbacks%2C%20in%20return%20for%20liquor%20licences.%20The%20agency%20has%20claimed%20the%20AAP%20received%20kickbacks%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore%20that%20was%20then%20used%20to%20fund%20its%20Goa%20and%20Punjab%20election%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20AAP%20and%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20have%20refused%20all%20charges%20and%20called%20the%20arrest%20and%20case%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20vendetta%26quot%3B%2C%20coming%20as%20it%20did%2C%20weeks%20before%20the%20election.%20The%20arrest%20also%20triggered%20a%20political%20spat%20between%20the%20ruling%20BJP%20and%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20which%20is%20led%20by%20the%20Congress%20and%20of%20which%20the%20AAP%20is%20a%20member.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716961920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F4t8b8ev8_arvind-kejriwal-ani-650_650x400_04_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwals-plea-for-extension-of-bail-wont-be-heard-by-supreme-court-5769345%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20not%20hear%20Arvind%20Kejriwal's%20request%20seeking%20a%207-day%20extension%20of%20his%20interim%20bail%20in%20a%20corruption%20case%20linked%20to%20the%20Delhi%20liquor%20policy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwals-plea-for-extension-of-bail-wont-be-heard-by-supreme-court-5769345%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwals-plea-for-extension-of-bail-wont-be-heard-by-supreme-court-5769345%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farvind-kejriwals-plea-for-extension-of-bail-wont-be-heard-by-supreme-court-5769345%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pune%20Teen's%20Father%2C%2