is%20university%20graduation.%20He%20said%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Binitially%20alarmed%20at%20the%20sight%20of%20someone%20charging%20towards%20the%20cockpit%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20per%20the%20outlet.%20Sterling%20claimed%20that%20when%20the%20man%20reportedly%20knocked%20over%20the%20flight%20attendant%2C%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20yelling%20and%20screaming%26quot%3B%20near%20the%20cockpit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInitially%20you%20think%2C%20God%20forbid%2C%20it%20could%20be%20an%20attack.%20It's%20really%20distressing%20being%20on%20a%20plane%20in%20that%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Sterling%20continued%2C%20%26quot%3BOne%20good%20Samaritan%2C%20this%20big%20guy%20in%20business%20class%2C%20jumped%20up%20straight%20away%20to%20intervene%20and%20then%20these%20two%20other%20guys%20later%20got%20up%20and%20tackled%20him%20to%20the%20ground.%26quot%3B%20He%20said%20the%20individual%20was%20pinned%20down%2C%20handcuffed%2C%20and%20taken%20to%20the%20back%20of%20the%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20allegedly%20%26quot%3Bsuddenly%20went%20bananas%20running%20up%20and%20down%20the%20aisle%20and%20bashing%20on%20the%20cockpit%20door%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20another%20passenger%20who%20had%20been%20on%20the%20flight.%20%26quot%3BTwo%20air%20marshals%20had%20to%20restrain%20and%20handcuff%20the%20individual%20until%20the%20%5Bflight%5D%20landed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20passenger%20told%20a%20radio%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unruly%20traveller%20was%20sent%20to%20a%20nearby%20hospital%20for%20evaluation%2C%20where%20he%20remained%20on%20Tuesday%20night.%20Although%20the%20accusations%20were%20still%20pending%2C%20it%20was%20anticipated%20that%20he%20would%20receive%20a%20summons%20to%20appear%20before%20the%20Perth%20magistrates%20court%20in%20June.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716961320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2Fpq6ojil_virgin-australia_625x300_06_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22origi