Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20With%20etymological%20roots%20in%20Arabic%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fphotos%2Fentertainment%2Fbollywoods-nautch-girls-8509%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0is%20a%20gesture%20of%20paying%20respects.%20While%20the%20term%20now%20refers%20to%20a%20dance%20of%20courtesans%2C%20the%20Arabic%20mothership%20phrase%C2%A0salam%20ma-jara%C2%A0literally%20translates%20as%20'greetings%20of%20praise%20that%20have%20been%20offered'.%20Because%20it%20is%20the%20rich%20and%20powerful%20that%20are%20worthy%20of%20exaggerated%20praise%2C%20women%20and%20men%20skilled%20in%20poetry%2C%20music%20and%20dance%20put%20up%20performances%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0in%20which%20they%20offered%C2%A0salam%C2%A0or%20salutations%20to%20their%20existing%20or%20potential%20patrons.%20Similar%20acts%20of%20paying%20respects%20were%20observed%20at%20Sufi%20shrines%2C%20both%20minor%20ones%20like%20that%20of%20Loh%20Langar%20Shah%20in%20Mangalore%2C%20and%20prominent%20ones%20like%20the%20resting%20place%20of%20Khwaja%20Moinuddin%20Chishti%20in%20Ajmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EPatronage%20As%20Power%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPatronage%20ensures%20survival.%20It%20is%20also%20the%20route%20to%20power.%20Nobody%20knows%20it%20better%20than%20women%20artists.%20One%20of%20the%20earliest%20women%20Urdu%20poets%2C%20Mah%20Laqa%20Bai%20of%20Hyderabad%2C%20was%20an%20adopted%20daughter%20of%20the%20prime%20minister%20of%20Deccan.%20Skilled%20in%20words%20and%20weaponry%20alike%2C%20she%20was%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20highest-ranking%20courtiers%20in%20the%20courts%20of%20the%20second%20and%20third%20Nizam%20of%20Hyderabad.%20One%20of%20the%20earliest%20recorded%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0performances%20dates%20back%20to%20September%2020%2C%201820.%20Mah%20Laqa%20Bai%20performed%20for%20Nizam%20Sikandar%20Asaf%20Jah%20at%20his%20Moti%20Mahal%20Palace.%20By%20this%20time%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0had%20become%20integral%20to%20the%20courtly%20savoir-faire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-priyanka-gandhi-vadra-pms-mujra-attack-on-india-bloc-priyanka-gandhis-decorum-reply-5743234%5C%22%3ERead%20%7C%C2%A0PM's%20%26quot%3BMujra%26quot%3B%20Attack%20On%20INDIA%20Bloc%2C%20Priyanka%20Gandhi's%20%26quot%3BDecorum%26quot%3B%20Reply%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%20performed%20by%20a%C2%A0tawaif%2C%20or%20courtesan%2C%20was%20a%20structured%20performance%20that%20began%20with%20a%20specific%20form%20of%20greeting-saluting%20seven%20times%20in%20a%20style%20similar%20to%20courtly%20salutations%20made%20to%20the%20king.%20The%20music%20and%20dance%20performance%20to%20entertain%20and%20pay%20obeisance%20to%20powerful%20patrons%2C%20together%20with%20this%C2%A0salami%2C%C2%A0which%20is%20the%20actual%20'%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E'%2C%20became%20known%20as%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0in%20common%20parlance.%20Again%2C%20contrary%20to%20popular%20notions%2C%20singing%20and%20not%20necessarily%20the%20dance%20was%20the%20central%20piece%20of%20a%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E.%20The%20tawaif%20sang%20either%20a%20ghazal%20or%20a%20Hindustani%20musical%20form%20like%20Dadra%2C%20Thumri%2C%20Hori%2C%20Kajri%20etc.%20Often%2C%20these%20performances%20were%20an%20occasion%20to%20showcase%20an%20upcoming%20poet's%20talents.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Real%20Mujra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20popular%20belief%2C%20a%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0performance%20is%20not%20necessarily%20a%20prequel%20to%20amorous%20or%20sexual%20liaisons.%20It%20may%2C%20however%2C%20lead%20to%20those%2C%20just%20like%20coffee%20dates.%20The%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0performances%20were%20stigmatised%20for%20various%20reasons%20even%20before%20the%C2%A0tawaifs%C2%A0descended%20hopelessly%20into%20the%20world%20of%20prostitution%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20British%20dismantling%20the%20Sultanate%20and%20regional%20courts.%20According%20to%20the%20records%20of%20Har%20Bilas%20Sarda%2C%20a%20civil%20servant%20writing%20in%20the%20early%20twentieth%20century%2C%20dancers%20and%20musicians%20-%20male%20and%20female%20-%20used%20to%20perform%20every%20Thursday%20at%20Khwaja%20Moinuddin%20Chishti's%20tomb%20in%20Ajmer.%20These%20musical%20assemblies%20were%20decried%20as%20%26quot%3Bsecular%20festivals%26quot%3B%20by%20religious%20fundamentalists.%20Despite%20resistance%20and%20attempts%20by%20even%20the%20shrine's%20management%2C%20these%20performances%20continued%20in%20Ajmer%20till%20the%201970s.%20Mujra%20wasn't%20Islamic%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20interesting%20fact%20about%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0involves%20the%20religion%20of%20the%20people%20concerned%20-%20performers%20as%20well%20as%20the%20audience.%20The%20patrons%20were%2C%20obviously%2C%20the%20rich%20and%20powerful%3B%20they%20could%20be%20Hindu%20zamindars%2C%20Sikh%20rulers%2C%20Christian%20British%20soldiers%2C%20or%20Muslim%20aristocracy.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20performers%20could%20be%20either%20Hindu%20or%20Muslim.%20The%20songs%20they%20sang%20could%20be%20in%20Persianate%20Urdu%20about%20courtly%20love%2C%20or%20in%20Brajbhasha%20about%20the%20divine%20love%20of%20Krishna%20and%20Radha.%20Kathak%2C%20the%20classical%20dance%20form%20associated%20with%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0is%20also%20the%20dance%20of%20devotion%2C%20with%20aesthetic%20roots%20in%20Bharat's%C2%A0Natyshastra.%20It%20is%20the%20Hindi%20film%20industry's%20fetishisation%20of%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0for%20its%20largely%20Hindu%20audience%20that%20seems%20to%20have%20rooted%20it%20solely%20in%20the%20Islamicate%20culture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMujra%20Has%20No%20Religion%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0performance%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20an%20arena%20where%20many%20patrons-men-used%20to%20compete%20for%20the%20favour%20of%20one%20woman%2C%20the%C2%A0tawaif.%20This%20asymmetry%20brought%20the%20aegis%20of%20power%20into%20the%20hands%20of%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20rather%20public%20fashion.%20The%20site%20of%20the%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20therefore%2C%20was%20also%20a%20site%20of%20subversion%20in%20a%20patriarchal%20society.%20The%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E-performing%C2%A0tawaifs%C2%A0were%20some%20of%20the%20most%20effective%20ground%20workers%20in%20India's%20freedom%20struggle.%20Their%20influence%2C%20resources%2C%20and%20access%20allowed%20revolutionaries%20to%20plan%20and%20execute%20their%20acts%20of%20resistance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0has%20become%20a%20metaphor%20for%20the%20practice%20of%20seeking%20benefits%20in%20return%20for%20sexual%20favours.%20Stripped%20of%20its%20cultural%20and%20aesthetic%20context%2C%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0can%20be%20any%20movement%20of%20the%20body%20in%20a%20sexually%20charged%20assembly.%20Even%20music%20is%20optional.%20It%20is%20this%20version%20of%C2%A0%3Cem%3Emujra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0that%20has%20crept%20into%20our%20socio-political%20imagination.%20The%20biggest%20problem%20with%20such%20a%20formulation%20is%20also%20the%20simplest%3A%20ignorance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EMujra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0is%20essentially%20Indian.%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMujra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0has%20no%20religion.%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMujra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0is%20subversive.%C2%A0%3Cem%3EMujra%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0is%20also%20like%20election%20time%2C%20a%20competitive%20site.%20The%20only%20difference%3A%20one%20voter%20is%20wooed%20by%20various%20vote-seekers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Nishtha%20Gautam%20is%20a%20Delhi-based%20author%20and%20academic.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%