A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-in-talks-with-paytm-to-acquire-stake-speculative-says-fintech-firm-124052900478_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNaveen%20Patnaik's%2025-Year%20Rule%20'Lost%20Years'%20Of%20Odisha%26quot%3B%3A%20Amit%20Shah%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHome%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20speaking%20exclusively%20with%20NDTV%2C%20slammed%20Odisha%20Chief%20Minister%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20nearly%2025-year%20tenure%20by%20terming%20it%20the%20%26quot%3Blost%20years%26quot%3B%20of%20Odisha.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20extensive%20campaigning%20in%20the%20coastal%20state%20has%20been%20spearheaded%20by%20heavyweights%20like%20Mr%20Shah%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20As%20Mr%20Patnaik%20inches%20closer%20to%20becoming%20the%20country's%20longest-serving%20chief%20minister%20by%20eclipsing%20former%20Arunachal%20Pradesh%20leader%20Pawan%20Chamling%2C%20the%20BJP%20aims%20to%20turn%20the%20tables%20and%20form%20government%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20history%20of%20this%20country%20is%20written%2C%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%2025-year%20rule%20will%20be%20known%20as%20the%20'lost%20years%20of%20Odisha'%2C%26quot%3B%20declared%20Mr%20Shah.%20%26quot%3BMany%20states%20in%20India%2C%20by%20improving%20their%20infrastructure%2C%20healthcare%2C%20economy%2C%20and%20agriculture%2C%20are%20now%20contributing%20massively%20to%20the%20country's%20economy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20pointed%20out%20that%20despite%20Odisha's%20rich%20mineral%20resources%2C%20the%20state%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20poorest%20in%20India.%20%26quot%3BSeveral%20states%20have%20done%20well%20in%20the%20last%2025%20years%20to%20eradicate%20poverty.%20In%20Odisha%2C%20before%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20'Har%20Ghar%20Nal%20Yojna'%2C%20only%204%20per%20cent%20of%20households%20had%20drinking%20water%20facilities.%20Odisha%20is%20India's%20most%20affluent%20state%20as%20it%20is%20blessed%20with%20huge%20quantities%20of%20minerals.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Odisha%20are%20the%20poorest%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20only%20reason%20behind%20this%20contradiction%20is%20Naveen%20%3Cem%3EBabu%3C%2Fem%3E's%20inaction%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20people%20of%20Odisha%20have%20seen%20the%20development%20of%20its%20neighbouring%20states%20and%20this%20time%2C%20most%20certainly%2C%20there%20will%20be%20a%20change%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EBJP's%20Vision%20For%20Odisha%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOutlining%20the%20BJP's%20plan%20for%20Odisha%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20stressed%20the%20need%20for%20better%20utilisation%20of%20the%20state's%20resources.%20%26quot%3BToday%20the%20youth%20of%20Odisha%20go%20out%20and%20work%20across%20the%20country.%20Odisha%20has%20a%20long%20coastline%2C%20it%20has%20rivers%20filled%20with%20water%20and%20hardworking%20people.%20If%20we%20make%20certain%20changes%20to%20agriculture%2C%20irrigation%2C%20and%20crop%20patenting%2C%20make%20the%20best%20use%20of%20its%20rich%20mines%20and%20minerals%2C%20and%20improve%20its%20infrastructure%20then%20within%20a%20short%20time%2C%20Odisha%20will%20be%20counted%20among%20the%20best-performing%20states%20in%20the%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Odisha%2C%20simultaneous%20elections%20are%20being%20held%2C%20and%20besides%20the%2021%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituencies%2C%20the%20147%20state%20Assembly%20seats%20are%20also%20going%20to%20polls%20in%20seven%20phases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20expressed%20confidence%20in%20the%20BJP's%20prospects%20in%20the%20upcoming%20elections%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20confident%20of%20winning%20at%20least%2017%20Lok%20Sabha%20seats%20and%2075%20Assembly%20seats%20in%20Odisha.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20whether%20Odisha%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bgreenfield%20project%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20BJP%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20affirmed%2C%20%26quot%3BIndeed.%20I%20have%20been%20witnessing%20a%20wave%20of%20change%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Not%20just%20in%20Odisha%2C%20but%20also%20in%20West%20Bengal%2C%20Telangana%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20and%20other%20states.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Ratna%20Bhandar%20Controversy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20also%20addressed%20the%20contentious%20issue%20of%20the%20missing%20keys%20to%20the%20Jagannath%20temple's%20Ratna%20Bhandar%20(treasury)%2C%20which%20has%20sparked%20a%20political%20row%20in%20Odisha.%20%26quot%3BThe%20mystery%20of%20the%20missing%20keys%20to%20Lord%20Jagannath's%20Ratna%20Bhandar%20is%20nowhere%20close%20to%20being%20solved.%20The%20keys%20were%20lost%2C%20a%20probe%20team%20was%20set%20up%2C%20and%20then%20someone%20alleged%20that%20fake%20keys%20were%20made.%20Was%20the%20Ratna%20Bhandar%20opened%20or%20not%3F%20No%20clarity%20has%20been%20offered%20by%20the%20Odisha%20government.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ratna%20Bhandar%2C%20opened%20only%20four%20times%20in%20the%20last%20century%2C%20has%20been%20central%20to%20the%20BJP's%20poll%20campaign%20in%20Odisha.%20%26quot%3BLord%20Jagannath's%20Ratna%20Bhandar%20is%20a%20subject%20that%20should%20not%20be%20shrouded%20in%20mystery%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Shah%20remarked.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Odisha%20government%20had%20in%202018%20appointed%20an%20inquiry%20commission%20under%20retired%20Orissa%20High%20Court%20judge%20Raghubir%20Dash%20to%20investigate%20the%20matter.%20Another%20panel%20under%20retired%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Arijit%20Pashayat%20was%20formed%20earlier%20this%20year%20following%20the%20Odisha%20High%20Court's%20directive%20to%20supervise%20the%20inventory%20process%20of%20the%20valuables%20stored%20in%20the%20Ratna%20Bhandar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EOn%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20Governance%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shah%20did%20not%20hold%20back%20in%20his%20criticism%20of%20Mr%20Patnaik's%20governance%2C%20describing%20it%20as%20a%20%3Cem%3E%26quot%3Bjhola%20chap%20sarkar%26quot%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20-%20a%20term%20implying%20incompetence%20and%20dependency.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20often%20call%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20government%20the%20'%3Cem%3Ejhola%20chap%20sarkaar'%3C%2Fem%3E%20because%20PM%20Modi%20gives%205%20kg%20rice%20to%20the%20poor%20in%20Odisha%20but%20Naveen%20Patnaik%20takes%20credit%20for%20that%20-%20our%20rice%2C%20his%20photo.%20Similarly%2C%20the%20PM%20Awaas%20Yojana%20and%20the%20Har%20Ghar%20Nal%20Yojana%20were%20given%20Odia%20names%20and%20taken%20credit%20for.%20Schemes%20are%20being%20formulated%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20but%20their%20credit%20is%20being%20taken%20by%20Naveen%20Patnaik.%20Naveen%3Cem%3E%20Babu%3C%2Fem%3E%20does%20not%20know%20that%20the%20people%20of%20Odisha%20are%20aware%20of%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EStrained%20Ties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20considered%20the%20BJP's%20most%20reliable%20ally%20in%20the%20NDA%2C%20the%20BJD-BJP%20alliance%20saw%20success%20in%20two%20assembly%20elections%20and%20three%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20in%20Odisha.%20The%20partnership%2C%20forged%20in%20February%201998%2C%20enjoyed%20a%20strong%20foundation%2C%20with%20both%20parties%20successfully%20contesting%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20in%201998%2C%201999%2C%20and%202004%2C%20as%20well%20as%20assembly%20elections%20in%202000%20and%202004.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alliance%20collapsed%20in%202009%20following%20failed%20seat-sharing%20talks.%20The%20breakdown%20was%20officially%20attributed%20to%20the%20BJD's%20demand%20for%20a%20reduction%20in%20the%20BJP's%20share%20of%20assembly%20seats%20from%2063%20to%20around%2040%2C%20and%20parliamentary%20seats%20from%20nine%20to%20six.%20This%20demand%2C%20deemed%20unreasonable%20by%20the%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20led%20to%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20support%20to%20Chief%20Minister%20Patnaik's%20government%2C%20marking%20the%20end%20of%20an%2011-year%20political%20marriage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20withdrawal%20of%20support%20was%20termed%20by%20BJD%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bact%20of%20betrayal%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716958380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fbidhmn38_amit-shah-interview-_625x300_29_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felections-2024-naveen-patnaiks-25-year-rule-lost-years-of-odisha-amit-shah-to-ndtv-5769157%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20speaking%20exclusively%20with%20NDTV%2C%20slammed%20Odisha%20Chief%20Minister%20Naveen%20Patnaik's%20nearly%2025-year%20tenure%20by%20terming%20it%20the%20%26quot%3Blost%20years%26quot%3B%20of%20Odisha.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felections-2024-naveen-patnaiks-25-year-rule-lost-years-of-odisha-amit-shah-to-ndtv-5769157%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felections-2024-naveen-patnaiks-25-year-rule-lost-years-of-odisha-amit-shah-to-ndtv-5769157%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felections-2024-naveen-patnaiks-25-year-rule-lost-years-of-odisha-amit-shah-to-ndtv-5769157%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22China%20Banker%20Gets%20Death%20Sentence%20For%20Taking%20Rs%201%2C264%20Crore%20In%20Bribes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBai%20Tianhai%2C%20former%20general%20manager%20of%20China%20Huarong%20International%20Holdings%20(CHIH)%2C%20who%20accepted%20bribes%20worth%20more%20than%201.1%20billion%20yuan%20(Rs%C2%A012%2C64%2C12%2C73%2C722)%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%20death%C2%A0by%20a%20court%20in%20eastern%20China.%20The%20court%20found%20that%20the%20former%20senior%20banker%20took%20advantage%20of%20his%20position%20to%20aid%20others%20in%20the%20acquisitions%20and%20financing%20of%20projects%20in%20exchange%20for%20huge%20sums%2C%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.scmp.com%2Fnews%2Fchina%2Fpolitics%2Farticle%2F3264499%2Fchina-hands-death-sentence-senior-banker-taking-us151-million-bribes%3Fmodule%3Dtop_story%26pgtype%3Dhomepage%5C%22%3ESouth%20China%20Morning%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20CHIH%2C%20an%20offshore%20unit%20of%20China%20Huarong%20Asset%20Management%20(CHAM)%2C%20was%20taken%20over%20by%20the%20Citic%20Group%20and%20renamed%20China%20Citic%20Financial%20Asset%20Management%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20the%20bribes%20the%20former%20banker%20had%20taken%20were%20''particularly%20huge''%20and%20the%20impacts%20of%20his%20crimes%20on%20society%20''particularly%20pernicious%2C%20causing%20%E2%80%A6%20serious%20losses%20to%20the%20interests%20of%20the%20state%20and%20the%20people''.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Taking%20all%20these%20%5Bfactors%5D%20into%20account%2C%20%5Bthe%20court%5D%20ruled%20that%20%5BBai%5D%20does%20not%20deserve%20a%20lighter%20sentence.%20Hence%20the%20death%20penalty%20verdict%2C''%20the%20ruling%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20ruling%2C%20the%20court%20ordered%20that%20all%20his%20personal%20property%20be%20confiscated.%20He%20was%20also%C2%A0permanently%20stripped%20of%20his%20political%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%C2%A0Tianhai%2C%20his%20ex-boss%20and%C2%A0former%20chairman%20of%20CHAM%2C%20also%20received%20a%20death%20sentence%20for%20corruption.%C2%A0In%20January%202021%2C%20the%20same%20court%20sentenced%20Lai%20Xiaomin%20after%20finding%20him%20guilty%20of%20taking%201.79%20billion%20yuan%20(US%24247%20million)%20in%20bribes%2C%20embezzlement%20of%20public%20assets%20worth%20more%20than%2025.13%20million%20yuan%20(US%243.46%20million)%2C%20and%20bigamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EXu%20Maiyong%20and%20Jiang%20Renjie%2C%20former%20mayors%20of%20the%20eastern%20cities%20of%20Hangzhou%2C%20in%20Zhejiang%20province%2C%20and%20Suzhou%20in%20Jiangsu%2C%20also%20received%20similar%20sentences.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20yet%20known%20if%C2%A0Tianhai%20would%20be%20appealing%20the%20sentence.%C2%A0A%20Beijing-based%20criminal%20lawyer%20said%20that%20he%20expects%20Bai%20to%20appeal%20on%20grounds%20of%20precedent%2C%20citing%20cases%20where%20defendants%20were%20given%20lesser%20sentences%20for%20similar%20offences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rare%20ruling%20comes%20after%C2%A0China's%20top%20corruption%20watchdog%2C%20the%20Central%20Commission%20for%20Discipline%20Inspection%20(CCDI)%20launched%20a%20crackdown%20on%20the%20finance%20sector%20this%20year%2C%20in%20response%20to%20Xi%20Jinping's%20call%20to%20make%20China%20a%20%26quot%3Bfinancial%20superpower%26quot%3B%20and%20contain%20risks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20should%20be%20%E2%80%9Cabsolutely%20no%20mercy%E2%80%9D%20in%20rooting%20out%20the%20%E2%80%9Csevere%20and%20complex%E2%80%9D%20problem%20of%20corruption%20and%20fraud%2C%20Xi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716958320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fcedaveng_bribe_625x300_29_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-banker-gets-death-sentence-for-taking-rs-1-264-crore-in-bribes-5769113%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20court%20found%20that%20the%20former%20senior%20banker%20took%20advantage%20of%20his%20position%20to%20aid%20others%20in%20the%20acquisitions%20and%20financing%20of%20projects%20in%20exchange%20for%20huge%20sums.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-banker-gets-death-sentence-for-taking-rs-1-264-crore-in-bribes-5769113%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fchina-banker-gets-death-sentence-for-taking-rs-1-264-crore-in-bribes-5769113%2Famp%2F1%22%2C