icleshow%2F110521256.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20took%20a%20break%20in%20Mumbai%20before%20the%20ICC%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20which%20starts%20on%20June%202.%20He%20was%20seen%20enjoying%20a%20dinner%20date%20with%20his%20wife%20Anushka%20Sharma%2C%20fellow%20cricketer%20Zaheer%20Khan%2C%20and%20cricket%20presenter%20Gaurav%20Kapur.%20The%20couple%20was%20seen%20leaving%20a%20trendy%20eatery%20in%20Bandra%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20according%20to%20an%20Instagram%20video.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-mens-t20-world-cup%2Fwatch-virat-kohli-enjoys-dinner-date-with-anushka-sharma-and-friends-in-mumbai-ahead-of-t20-world-cup%2Farticleshow%2F110521256.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Teen%20Behind%20Pune%20Porsche%20Crash%20Had%20Driven%2C%20Illegally%2C%20A%20Day%20Earlier%20Too%3A%20Cops%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMay%2019%2C%20when%20a%2017-year-old%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20Pune%20realtor%20rammed%20his%20Porsche%20into%20two%20techies%20in%20their%2020s%20-%20killing%20them%20on%20the%20spot%20-%20was%20not%20the%20first%20time%20he%20was%20illegally%20driving%20a%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20has%20emerged%20from%20just%20a%20day%20before%20the%20horrific%20tragedy%2C%20showing%20the%20teenager%20emerging%20from%20the%20driver's%20side%20of%20a%20car%20while%20attending%20a%20college%20event.%20The%20video%20shows%20the%20boy%20getting%20out%20off%20the%20car%2C%20accompanied%20by%20a%20male%20friend%20who%20seemed%20to%20be%20in%20the%20passenger%20seat%2C%20as%20three%20girls%20appear%20to%20wait%20for%20them%20in%20the%20foreground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girls%20are%20joined%20by%20three%20other%20boys%20and%20the%20teenager%20and%20his%20friend%20walk%20up%20to%20them%20and%20greet%20them%20before%20entering%20the%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20sources%20have%20confirmed%20that%20the%20teenager%20was%20driving%20a%20car%20on%20the%20day%20of%20the%20college%20event.%20Just%20hours%20later%2C%20he%20went%20partying%20-%20in%20a%20Rs%202.5-crore%20Porsche%20-%20with%20his%20friends%20to%20celebrate%20his%20Class%2012%20results%20(in%20Maharashtra%20Class%2011%20and%2012%20students%20attend%20what%20is%20called%20a%20junior%20college).%20They%20went%20to%20two%20pubs%20and%20drank%20illegally%2C%20and%20he%20racked%20up%20a%20bill%20of%20Rs%2048%2C000%20at%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20teen%20then%20got%20into%20the%20Porsche%20with%20two%20of%20his%20friends%20and%20crashed%20into%20the%20scooter%20in%20Pune's%20Kalyani%20Nagar%20at%20a%20speed%20of%20at%20least%20150%20kmph%2C%20killing%20two%2024-year-old%20IT%20professionals%20on%20the%20spot.%20Aneesh%20Awadhiya%2C%20who%20was%20riding%20the%20bike%20was%20sent%20flying%20and%20hit%20a%20parked%20car%2C%20while%20Ashwini%20Koshta%20-%20who%20was%20riding%20pillion%20-%20was%20flung%2020%20feet%20into%20the%20air.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20Maharashtra%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%20said%20the%20law%20is%20equal%20for%20all%20and%20no%20one%20would%20be%20spared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnswering%20a%20question%20on%20the%20alleged%20preferential%20treatment%20given%20to%20the%2017-year-old%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20Pune%20builder%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20said%20in%20Hindi%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20been%20in%20touch%20with%20the%20Pune%20police%20commissioner%20since%20day%20one.%20I%20have%20said%20right%20from%20the%20beginning%20that%2C%20irrespective%20of%20how%20influential%20the%20person%20is%2C%20there%20should%20be%20no%20discrimination.%20No%20matter%20how%20rich%20or%20poor%20a%20person%20is%2C%20the%20law%20is%20equal%20for%20all%20and%20no%20one%20will%20be%20spared.%20I%20have%20ordered%20strict%20action.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20two%20people%20who%20have%20died%20are%20also%20someone's%20children.%20Strict%20action%20will%20be%20taken%20against%20all%20guilty%20people%20in%20this%20case.%20Their%20background%20will%20also%20be%20checked.%20I%20have%20personally%20told%20the%20police%20commissioner%20to%20spare%20no%20one%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20a%20doctor%20or%20anyone%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shinde%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20arrest%20of%20Dr%20Ajay%20Tawade%20and%20Dr%20Hari%20Harnor%20of%20Sasoon%20Hospital%20by%20the%20Pune%20Crime%20Branch%20for%20allegedly%20replacing%20the%20teenager's%20blood%20samples%20with%20those%20of%20a%20doctor%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20alcohol%20was%20detected%20in%20them.%20A%20peon%2C%20Atul%20Ghatkamble%2C%20who%20acted%20as%20the%20middleman%20and%20allegedly%20collected%20the%20%E2%82%B9%203%20lakh%20bribe%20meant%20for%20the%20two%20doctors%20from%20the%20realtor's%20family%2C%20was%20also%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiv%20Sena%20leader's%20remarks%20had%20come%20after%20the%20Congress's%20Maharashtra%20unit%20President%2C%20Nana%20Patole%2C%20had%20alleged%20that%20the%20son%20of%20an%20MLA%20was%20also%20involved%20in%20the%20accident%20and%20the%20legislator%20had%20taken%20part%20in%20the%20cover-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Congress%20leader%20did%20not%20name%20the%20legislator%2C%20there%20have%20been%20reports%20of%20Sunil%20Tingre%20-%20the%20NCP%20(Ajit%20Pawar%20faction)%20MLA%20from%20Vadgaonsheri%20-%20having%20visited%20the%20Yerwada%20police%20station%2C%20where%20the%20teenager%20was%20taken%20after%20the%20accident%2C%20in%20the%20early%20hours%20of%20May%2019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20boy%20will%20be%20in%20a%20remand%20home%20till%20June%205.%20His%20father%20and%20grandfather%20are%20in%20police%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716957900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Feoj00p2o_pune-porsche-_625x300_22_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news