0Tata%20to%20treat%20these%20animals%20well%20if%20they%20enter%20the%20premises%2C%26quot%3B%20Rubi%20wrote%20in%20her%20LinkedIn%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fembed%2Ffeed%2Fupdate%2Furn%3Ali%3Ashare%3A7200517135750610944%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Embedded%20post%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221127%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khan%20went%20on%20to%20describe%20how%20this%20encounter%20touched%20her%20and%20said%2C%26quot%3BWhat%20inspired%20me%20to%20write%20this%20is%20the%20realisation%20that%20this%20place%2C%20home%20to%20numerous%20guests%20ranging%20from%20political%20dignitaries%20to%20national%20and%20international%20celebrities%2C%20values%20every%20being%20within%20its%20walls.%20The%20entrance%20of%20such%20a%20prestigious%20establishment%20holds%20significant%20importance%2C%20and%20there%20he%20was%2C%20peacefully%20sleeping%2C%20perhaps%20unnoticed%20by%20many%20of%20the%20guests.%20Amidst%20the%20chaos%2C%20he%20owns%20the%20place%2C%20finding%20his%20sanctuary.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20scenario%20highlighted%20a%20profound%20truth%20for%20me%3A%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20leading%20and%20driving%20business%20while%20being%20customer-obsessed%2C%20the%20true%20soul%20of%20a%20business%20is%20reflected%20in%20how%20it%20treats%20others.%20We%20often%20speak%20about%20inclusion%2C%20biases%2C%20psychological%20safety%2C%20and%20emotional%20intelligence.%20I%20witnessed%20all%20these%20principles%20in%20action%20here.%20It's%20a%20fine%20balance%20of%20head%20and%20heart%2C%20being%20authentic%2C%20and%20not%20worrying%20about%20what%20others%20might%20think%20as%20they%20enter%20this%20esteemed%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20has%20gone%20extremely%20viral%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20and%20people%20are%20appreciating%20the%20gesture%20by%20the%20Tata%20group%20and%20Ratan%20Tata