hin%20the%20state.%20Their%20significant%20investments%20in%20street%20cleaning%20have%20placed%20them%20amongst%20the%20cleaner%20half%20of%20US%20cities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20goes%20beyond%20air%20quality.%20Dirty%20drinking%20water%20plagues%20the%20southwest%2C%20with%20every%20major%20city%20except%20Salt%20Lake%20City%20violating%20the%20Safe%20Drinking%20Water%20Act%20in%202020.%20Las%20Vegas%2C%20ranking%2019th%20dirtiest%20overall%2C%20suffers%20from%20the%20most%20unsafe%20water%20in%20the%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20study%20also%20sheds%20light%20on%20a%20unique%20littering%20trend.%20Ohio%20takes%20the%20cake%20for%20cigarette%20butt%20litter%2C%20with%20five%20of%20its%20cities%20boasting%20the%20highest%20number%20of%20smokers.%20This%20littering%20issue%20persists%20despite%20local%20anti-smoking%20campaigns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20coastal%20cities%20tend%20to%20be%20cleaner%2C%20with%20Virginia%20Beach%20topping%20the%20%26quot%3Bmost%20pristine%26quot%3B%20list.%20However%2C%20proximity%20to%20water%20doesn't%20guarantee%20cleanliness%20-%20Fremont%2C%20California%2C%20and%20Winston-Salem%2C%20North%20Carolina%2C%20both%20rank%20highly%20despite%20being%20inland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELawnStarter's%20study%20paints%20a%20complex%20picture%20of%20cleanliness%20in%20the%20US.%20Big-city%20grime%20isn't%20the%20only%20story%20-%20air%20quality%2C%20pests%2C%20and%20even%20drinking%20water%20quality%20vary%20significantly%20across%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716951480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fikkjmla_houston-texas_625x300_29_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fhouston-new-york-this-us-city-steals-dirtiest-city-crown-exposing-grime-under-americas-shine-5768524%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20LawnStarter%20study%20reveals%20Houston%20as%20America's%20dirtiest%20city%2C%20surpassing%20Newark%2C%20while%20New%20York%20City%2