p%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGutman's%20popularity%20grew%20rapidly%20over%20the%20years%20since%20her%20account%20was%20first%20created%2C%20in%20part%20due%20to%20her%20exposure%20on%20TLC's%20%26quot%3BSay%20Yes%20to%20the%20Dress%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20spin-off%20%26quot%3BSay%20Yes%20to%20America%26quot%3B%20from%202015%20to%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20complaint%2C%20JLM%20claimed%20it%20was%20responsible%20for%20Gutman's%20growing%20fame%2C%20as%20Murphy%20arranged%20for%20Gutman%20to%20appear%20on%20the%20show%20because%20of%20%26quot%3Bhis%20connection%20at%20Kleinfeld%20Bridal%2C%20one%20of%20JLM's%20biggest%20customers%20and%20the%20location%20where%20'Say%20Yes%20to%20the%20Dress'%20is%20taped.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20the%20same%20month%2C%20Gutman%20created%20a%20TikTok%20account%20with%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20handle%2C%20according%20to%20a%20complaint%20filed%20by%20JLM's%20attorneys.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayleypaige%20tiktok%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ff4c5666d61c10019ccdcfd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224329%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screenshot%20of%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20TikTok%20account.%3Cp%3E%40misshayleypaige%2FTikTok%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20joined%20TikTok%20%E2%80%94%20using%C2%A0the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40misshayleypaige%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%3E%40misshayleypaige%3C%2Fa%3E%20handle%20%E2%80%94%20on%20November%202%2C%202019%2C%20according%20to%20JLM's%20complaint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20designer%20used%20the%20platform%20to%20post%20personal%20videos%20alongside%20bridal%20content.%20A%20screenshot%20of%20the%20page%20from%20January%202021%20shows%20videos%20of%20Gutman's%20dog%2C%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%2C%20and%20Hayley%20Paige%20gowns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJLM%20said%20that%20the%20mixed%20style%20of%20posts%20%26quot%3Bdid%20not%20properly%20represent%20the%20HP%20brands%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20December%202020%20complaint%20its%20attorneys%20filed%20against%20Gutman%2C%20adding%20that%20people%20who%20follow%20Hayley%20Paige-branded%20social-media%20accounts%20%26quot%3Bdo%20so%20because%20they%20want%20to%20follow%20JLM's%20Hayley%20Paige%20Brand%20designer%20wedding%20gown%20collection.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESome%20time%20after%2C%20JLM%20Couture%20CEO%20Joe%20Murphy%20advised%20Gutman%20to%20post%20company-approved%20social-media%20posts%20as%20they%20began%20discussing%20a%20new%20contract%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hayley%20Paige%20Gutman%20Getty%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fe49a0cedf8920018093a2e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20and%20JLM%20disagreed%20over%20the%20use%20of%20social-media%20accounts%20affiliated%20with%20her%20bridal%20brands.%3Cp%3EBrent%20N.%20Clarke%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJoe%20Murphy%20advised%20Gutman%20that%20she%20should%20post%20JLM%20approved%20content%20on%20the%20Tik%20Tok%20account%2C%20rather%20than%20posting%20personal%20images%2C%26quot%3B%20JLM's%20complaint%20against%20Gutman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company's%20complaint%20said%20that%20rather%20than%20complying%2C%20Gutman%20retaliated%2C%20changing%20the%20password%20to%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20account%20to%20prevent%20JLM%20from%20accessing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Gutman%20and%20JLM%20entered%20into%20discussions%20about%20a%20new%20contract%2C%20with%20use%20of%20the%20name%20%26quot%3BHayley%20Paige%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20center%20of%20many%20of%20the%20negotiations%2C%20according%20to%20JLM's%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJLM%20%26quot%3Bbelieved%20that%20Gutman's%20decision%20to%20take%20over%20the%20Main%20IG%20Account%20%5B%40misshayleypaige%5D%20was%20a%20negotiation%20tactic%20to%20obtain%20leverage%26quot%3B%20as%20she%20renegotiated%20her%20contract%20with%20the%20company%2C%20the%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202019%2C%20Gutman%20removed%20references%20and%20links%20to%20JLM%20from%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20Instagram%20account's%20bio%2C%20the%20complaint%20said.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221997%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hayley%20Paige%20Gutman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fe210bed366e60018099959%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221498%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJLM's%20complaint%20said%20that%20Gutman%20used%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20Instagram%20account%20like%20an%20influencer.%3Cp%3EInstagram%2Fallthatglittersonthegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20changed%20the%20bio%20of%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20Instagram%20account%20to%20read%20%26quot%3BPersonal%20%26amp%3B%20Creative%20account%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bremoved%20reference%20to%20JLM%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20end%20of%202019%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20complaint%20said%20that%20the%20bio%20changes%20marked%20Gutman's%20attempt%20to%20%26quot%3Bassert%20control%20over%20JLM's%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20led%20her%20to%20post%20more%20non-bridal%20related%20content%20to%20the%20Instagram%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EIn%20June%202020%2C%20Gutman%20told%20JLM%20she%20believed%20she%20owned%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20Instagram%20account%2C%20according%20to%20the%20complaint.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221778%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%20gutman%202%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fea32a5a644880018193889%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20believes%20she%20owns%20the%20account.%3Cp%3EDia%20Dipasupil%20%2F%20Staff%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Gutman%20and%20Murphy%20discussed%20her%20use%20of%20the%20social-media%20page%2C%20she%20told%20him%20that%20%26quot%3Bit%20was%20her%20position%20that%20the%20Main%20IG%20Account%20was%20her%20personal%20account%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGutman's%20position%20regarding%20the%20ownership%20of%20the%20Main%20IG%20Account%20was%20not%20only%20new%2C%20but%20Gutman%20at%20all%20times%20previously%20mentioned%20%5Bshe%5D%20understood%20that%20the%20Main%20IG%20account%20was%20JLM's%20properly%20%5Bsic%5D%20and%20acted%20accordingly%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20complaint%20went%20on%20to%20say.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20denied%20these%20allegations%20in%20both%20a%20statement%20to%20BI%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJD7CIbn7UN%2F%5C%22%3Ean%20Instagram%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20asserting%20that%20the%20account%20has%20always%20been%20hers%2C%20pointing%20to%20personal%20announcements%20she%20made%20on%20the%20page%2C%20such%20as%20that%20of%20her%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJLM's%20complaint%20said%20Gutman%20began%20posting%20ads%20for%20other%20companies%20and%20products%20on%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20Instagram%20account%20in%20July%202020.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221624%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%20sponcon%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fea2517a644880018193831%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221196%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20post%20on%20the%20Hayley%20Paige%20Instagram%20account%20promotes%20goods%20from%20another%20company.%3Cp%3EHayley%20Paige%20Gutman%2FJLM%20Couture%2FInstagram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20summer%20of%202020%2C%20Gutman%20was%20not%20only%20sharing%20personal%20posts%20to%20the%20page%20but%20also%20posts%20dedicated%20to%20products%20not%20sold%20by%20JLM%2C%20according%20to%20the%20company's%20complaint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E