s%20with%20the%20same%20handle%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20December%2015%2C%202020%2C%20JLM%20sued%20Gutman%20over%20her%20use%20of%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20Instagram%20account.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%20gutman%20sytd%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fea3fe5edf8920018093eee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJLM%20sued%20Gutman%20over%20her%20use%20of%20social%20media%20affiliated%20with%20her%20brands.%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSay%20Yes%20To%20The%20Dress%26quot%3B%2FTLC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20issues%20between%20Gutman%20and%20JLM%20came%20to%20a%20head%20in%20December%202020%2C%20with%20JLM%20suing%20the%20designer%20over%20her%20use%20of%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20Instagram%20account%20%26quot%3Bas%20her%20own%20business%20platform%20as%20if%20she%20were%20an%20influencer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company's%20complaint%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20Hayley%20stopped%20posting%20JLM%20content%20and%20deprived%20the%20company%20access%20to%20the%20account%2C%20we%20brought%20the%20matter%20before%20the%20court%2C%26quot%3B%20JLM%20wrote%20in%20a%20statement%20provided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpagesix.com%2F2020%2F12%2F21%2Fwedding-gown-designer-hayley-paige-weeps-over-bitter-dispute-with-bosses%2F%5C%22%3EPage%20Six%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20the%20time.%20%26quot%3BAfter%20carefully%20listening%20to%20both%20sides%2C%20a%20judge%20granted%20us%20the%20Temporary%20Restraining%20Order%20(TRO).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20order%20prevented%20Gutman%20from%20posting%20on%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20accounts%20without%20approval%20from%20JLM%2C%20and%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20turn%20over%20passwords%20for%20the%20Instagram%2C%20Pinterest%2C%20and%20TikTok%20page%2C%20according%20to%20a%20statement%20JLM%20provided%20to%20BI%20on%20December%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20respect%20the%20judge's%20decision%20that%20JLM%20should%20have%20temporary%20control%20over%20the%20company%20site%20and%20feel%20the%20process%20was%20fair%20and%20equitable%2C%26quot%3B%20JLM's%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDays%20later%2C%20on%20December%2021%2C%202020%2C%20Gutman%20released%20a%20video%20announcing%20her%20resignation%20from%20JLM%20on%20her%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%20Instagram%20account.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%20gutman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fea2e87edf8920018093eb5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222197%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman's%20December%2021%20Instagram%20video%20went%20viral.%3Cp%3EHayley%20Paige%20Gutman%2FInstagram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2021%2C%202020%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvideo-wedding-dress-designer-hayley-paige-banned-from-instagram-account-2020-12%5C%22%3EGutman%20announced%20her%20resignation%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20JLM%20to%20her%20followers%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJD7CIbn7UN%2F%5C%22%3Ea%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20posted%20on%20her%20Instagram%20account%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fallthatglittersonthegram%2F%5C%22%3E%40allthatglittersonthegram%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20isn't%20associated%20with%20JLM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20with%20a%20heavy%20heart%20that%20I%20have%20resigned%20from%20my%20role%20as%20head%20designer%20of%20my%20labels%20with%20JLM%20Couture%2C%26quot%3B%20Gutman%20wrote%20in%20the%20caption.%20%26quot%3BGoing%20forward%2C%20I%20will%20no%20longer%20be%20associated%20with%20any%20of%20their%20products%2C%20including%20the%20designs%20and%20dresses%20which%20bear%20my%20name.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaking%20their%20legal%20dispute%20public%2C%20Gutman%20said%20in%20her%20video%20that%20JLM%20convinced%20a%20court%20to%20ba