r%20discussed%20the%20ramifications%20of%20having%20JLM%20own%20the%20Hayley%20Paige%20name%20and%20requested%20to%20be%20compensated%20for%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20press%20release%20said.%20%26quot%3BJLM%20agreed%20to%20the%20request%20and%20increased%20Hayley's%20compensation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20December%2023%2C%202020%2C%20JLM%20posted%20a%20statement%20on%20Instagram%20to%20publicly%20defend%20the%20company%20against%20Gutman's%20claims.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%20gutman%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ff4a5dd3793140019e286c2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221499%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJLM%20posted%20a%20public%20statement%20to%20Instagram.%3Cp%3ECindy%20Ord%20%2F%20Stringer%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjlm-couture-responds-to-hayley-paige-on-instagram-2020-12%5C%22%3EJLM%20addressed%20the%20backlash%3C%2Fa%3E%20it%20was%20receiving%20after%20Gutman%20published%20her%20video%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJJMfAZD8-G%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%5C%22%3Ean%20Instagram%20post%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20was%20first%20posted%20to%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20account%2C%20but%20it%20was%20then%20promptly%20deleted%20and%20reposted%20to%20the%20JLM%20corporate%20account%20%E2%80%94%20a%20mix-up%20that%20was%20down%20to%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20error%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20representative%20for%20the%20company%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLike%20many%20things%20that%20glitter%20and%20shine%2C%20the%20issues%20between%20JLM%20Couture%20and%20Hayley%20Paige%20Gutman%20are%20multifaceted%2C%26quot%3B%20JLM's%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20we%20were%20shocked%20and%20heartbroken%20to%20see%20Hayley's%20video%2C%20we%20feel%20that%20the%20correct%20negotiations%20she%20referred%20to%20are%20a%20private%20matter%20between%20those%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20in%20this%20case%20between%20Hayley%20and%20Joe%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20continued%2C%20referring%20to%20JLM's%20CEO%20Joe%20Murphy.%20%26quot%3BBut%20in%20light%20of%20some%20of%20Hayley's%20comments%20in%20the%20video%2C%20we%20feel%20compelled%20to%20address%20a%20few%20points.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFirst%2C%20it%20is%20documented%20that%20Hayley%20had%20a%20lawyer%20help%20her%20review%20her%20employment%20contracts.%20She%20consulted%20with%20her%20lawyer%20prior%20to%20signing%20the%20contracts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%20%26quot%3BThere%20were%20multiple%20rounds%20of%20negotiations%20between%20Hayley%20and%20JLM%20until%20both%20parties%20settled%20on%20an%20agreement%20each%20felt%20was%20fair%20and%20mutually%20beneficial.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecond%2C%20Hayley%20has%20access%20to%20the%20social%20media%20accounts%20and%20JLM%20encourages%20and%20would%20welcome%20Hayley%20to%20continue%20contributing%20content%20that%20is%20supportive%20of%20the%20Hayley%20Paige%20brands%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BThird%2C%20we%20respectfully%20ask%20that%20you%20allow%20Hayley%2C%20Joe%20and%20their%20attorneys%20to%20discuss%20the%20details%20of%20negotiations%20privately.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20December%2024%2C%202020%2C%20Gutman%20took%20to%20Instagram%20to%20thank%20her%20fans%20for%20their%20support.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%20gutman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ff4a3593793140019e286ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221502%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20thanked%20her%20fans%20for%20their%20support.%3Cp%3EDia%20Dipasupil%20%2F%20Staff%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E