%2FInstagram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2028%2C%20JLM%20Couture%20provided%20Business%20Insider%20with%20an%20email%20that%20appeared%20to%20refute%20Gutman's%20claim%20that%20she%20didn't%20have%20a%20lawyer%20review%20her%20initial%20employment%20agreement%20with%20the%20fashion%20company%20in%202011.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjlm-email-appears-to-show-hayley-paige-saying-had-lawyer-2020-12%5C%22%3Ethe%20designer%20told%20Business%20Insider%20she%20signed%20the%20agreement%20without%20an%20attorney%20looking%20at%20it.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20email%20from%20an%20unnamed%20person%20at%20JLM%20(the%20person's%20name%20and%20part%20of%20their%20email%20address%20were%20redacted)%20read%3A%20%26quot%3BAttached%20is%20a%20signed%20contract.%20Hayley%20please%20confirm%20you%20have%20reviewed%20this%20with%20your%20attorney.%26quot%3B%20Business%20Insider%20was%20unable%20to%20review%20the%20document%20that%20appears%20to%20be%20attached%20to%20the%20email%3B%20the%20contract%20was%20sealed%20by%20court%20order.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20email%20address%20was%20redacted%20%E2%80%94%20appeared%20to%20respond%3A%20%26quot%3BThank%20you%20for%20sending!%20I%20have%20reviewed%20with%20my%20attorney%20accordingly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJLM's%20representative%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20Gutman%20was%20%26quot%3Bmisleading%20the%20public%20and%20her%20fans%20when%20she%20falsely%20claimed%20that%20she%20had%20no%20lawyer%20when%20she%20negotiated%20her%20first%20contract.%20Indeed%2C%20JLM%20insisted%20she%20have%20a%20lawyer%20and%20she%20did%20have%20a%20lawyer%20for%20her%20first%20%E2%80%93%20and%20every%20%E2%80%93%20contract%20negotiation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Gutman%20told%20Business%20Insider%20the%20email%20was%20sent%20after%20she%20had%20already%20signed%20the%20contract.%20%26quot%3BDespite%20what%20JLM%20claims%2C%20I%20di