56b60018721b84%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20shared%20a%20second%20update%20with%20her%20Instagram%20followers.%3Cp%3EHayley%20Paige%20Gutman%2FInstagram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJZqicJHOR9%2F%5C%22%3Ean%20Instagram%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20posted%20on%20December%2029%2C%202020%2C%20Gutman%20said%20she%20requested%20through%20her%20lawyers%20that%20JLM%20%26quot%3Bpause%20the%20litigation%20and%20start%20a%20conversation%20about%20a%20graceful%20end%26quot%3B%20to%20their%20professional%20relationship%2C%20as%20well%20as%20drop%20the%20temporary%20restraining%20order%20against%20her%20for%2060%20days.%20Gutman%20also%20requested%20that%20she%20be%20given%20back%20the%20rights%20to%20her%20name%2C%20as%20well%20as%20sole%20control%20of%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20social-media%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20December%2030%2C%20Gutman's%20representative%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20JLM%20refused%20to%20resume%20negotiations%20%26quot%3Band%20set%20multiple%20untenable%20preconditions%20before%20even%20returning%20to%20negotiations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20response%20indicates%20their%20decision%20to%20ignore%20the%20will%20of%20their%20bridal%20salon%20customers%20and%20their%20ultimate%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20same%20representative%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20confident%20justice%20will%20prevail.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhayley-paige-offers-to-resolve-differences-with-jlm-couture-terms-2020-12%5C%22%3EJLM's%20representative%20told%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it%20is%20%26quot%3Bblatantly%20untrue%26quot%3B%20that%20the%20company%20declined%20Gutman's%20offer.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20repeatedly%20reached%20out%20to%20Hayley's%20legal%20team%20and%2C%20without%20preconditions%2C%20told%20them%20we%20want%20to%20talk%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20said.%20%26quot%3BJLM%20remains%20committed%20to%20resolving%20the%20differences%20between%20the%20parties%2C%20but%20to%20do%20that%20Hayley%20and%20her%20team%20will%20need%20to%20engage%20in%20conversations%20with%20us.%20We%20hope%20that%20Hayley's%20public%20statements%20of%20wanting%20to%20negotiate%20are%20sincere%2C%20and%20if%20they%20are%20we%20look%20forward%20to%20having%20those%20conversations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGutman%20announced%20she%20filed%20an%20official%20response%20to%20JLM's%20lawsuit%20on%20January%2012%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%20counter%20suit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5fff0357fe7e140019f7ea48%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20legally%20responded%20to%20JLM's%20lawsuit.%3Cp%3E%40allthatglittersonthegram%2FInstagram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20filing%2C%20which%20Business%20Insider%20reviewed%2C%20Gutman%20asserted%20that%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20account%20was%20always%20her%20personal%20account%2C%20providing%20years'%20worth%20of%20screenshots%20as%20evidence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20own%20declaration%20that%20was%20filed%20with%20the%20response%2C%20Gutman%20stated%20that%20she%20started%20two%20social-media%20accounts%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Facebook%20page%20in%202004%20and%20a%20Twitter%20account%20in%202009%20%E2%80%94%20with%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20handle%20before%20she%20started%20working%20with%20JLM.%20She%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20her%20first%20six%20Instagram%20posts%20were%20personal%20in%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20response%20noted%20that%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20account%20was%20verified%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20figure%26quot%3B%20account%20in%202017%2C%20making%20it%20an%20account%20for%20a%20person%20rather%20than%20a%20company%2C%20though%20the%20page%20was%20later%20changed%20to%20be%20verified%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bclothing%20brand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20filing%20went%20on%20to%20provide%20declarations%20from%20JLM%20employees%20who%20viewed%20the%20account%20as%20Gutman's%20personal%20page%2C%20as%20well%20as%20emails%20from%20employees%20who%20referred%20to%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20account%20as%20Gutman's%20page.%20The%20documents%20also%20included%20an%20excerpt%20of%20an%20email%20from%20Murphy%20regarding%20his%20view%20of%20the%20company's%20ownership%20of%20the%20Hayley%20Paige%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20far%20as%20%5Byour%5D%20personal%20investment%20(regarding%20JLM)%20it%20really%20is%20only%20related%20to%20Hayley%20Paige%20wedding%20gowns%20and%20related%20categories%2C%26quot%3B%20Murphy%20wrote%20to%20Gutman%20via%20email%20in%202019.%20%26quot%3BRest%20assured%2C%20I%20do%20not%20claim%20access%20to%20your%20persona%20beyond%20what%20I%20describe%20above.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20motion%20claimed%20that%20the%20followers%20of%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20Instagram%20account%20noticed%20when%20JLM%20took%20over%20posting%20to%20the%20page%20for%20Gutman%20and%20commented%20messages%20supporting%20Gutman%2C%20indicating%20the%20page%20was%20not%20the%20same%20without%20her%20personal%20voice.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Gutman%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20always%20taken%20my%20contractual%20obligations%20seriously%2C%20and%20lived%20up%20to%20every%20one%20of%20them%2C%20but%20for%20JLM%20that%20was%20not%20enough.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BToday's%20response%20is%20my%20first%20opportunity%20to%20describe%20to%20the%20Court%20the%20misrepresentations%20and%20false%20claims%20that%20JLM%20Couture%20made%20in%20their%20emergency%20filing%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20believe%20that%20upon%20review%20of%20all%20of%20the%20facts%2C%20justice%20will%20be%20done.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20shared%20the%20news%20of%20the%20response%20with%20her%20followers%20in%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCJ9oROBnLnM%2F%5C%22%3E%20an%20Instagram%20video%20on%20January%2012%2C%202021%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20she%20even%20added%20a%20link%20to%20the%20lawsuit%20to%20the%20bio%20of%20the%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%20Instagram%20page%2C%20allowing%20her%20followers%20to%20look%20at%20the%20document.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20want%20you%20to%20take%20this%20journey%20along%20with%20me%2C%20and%20I%20have%20always%20valued%20transparency%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20why%20she%20added%20the%20link.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20January%2022%2C%202021%2C%20JLM%20filed%20a%20memorandum%20in%20support%20of%20its%20temporary%20restraining%20order.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%20gutman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F600f0533cf23090019e9720f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221503%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJLM%20doubled%20down%20on%20its%20claims.%3Cp%3EMireya%20Acierto%20%2F%20Contributor%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJLM%20filed%20papers%20directly%20refuting%20the%20claims%20Gutman%20made%20against%20the%20company%20in%20her%20response%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memorandum%20doubled%20down%20on%20JLM's%20stance%20that%20Gutman%20was%20never%20the%20owner%20of%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20social-media%20accounts%2C%20arguing%20that%20the%20existence%20of%20personal%20posts%20on%20the%20main%20Instagram%20account%20did%20not%20indicate%20that%20she%20owned%20the%20page.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20submitted%20300%20photos%20in%20her%20filing%20to%20demonstrate%20that%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20account%20was%20personal%20in%20nature%2C%20but%20the%20JLM%20team%20noted%20that%20the%20account%20had%205%2C879%20posts%20at%20the%20time%2C%20which%20meant%2095%25%20of%20the%20posts%20were%20business-related.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELikewise%2C%20the%20memorandum%20pointed%20to%20instances%20in%20which%20Gutman%20got%20approval%20from%20JLM%20or%20Murphy%20for%20what%20language%20she%20should%20use%20in%20non-bridal-related%20posts%2C%20including%20a%20post%20she%20made%20about%20her%20divorce%2C%20which%20JLM%20cited%20as%20evidence%20that%20Gutman%20thought%20the%20page%20was%20owned%20by%20the%20company.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20the%20memorandum%20addressed%20the%20emails%20Gutman%20included%20in%20her%20briefing%20from%20JLM%20employees%20who%20referred%20to%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20Instagram%20as%20her%20account%2C%20writing%20that%20those%20employees%20were%20not%20%26quot%3Bin%20positions%20where%20they%20were%20privy%20to%20the%20details%20regarding%20JLM's%20contractual%20arrangements%20with%2C%20assignment%20of%20duties%20to%20or%20acquisition%20of%20rights%20from%20Gutman.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memorandum%20also%20noted%20that%20Gutman's%20%26quot%3Bfalse%20and%20misleading%20smear%20campaign%20against%20JLM%26quot%3B%20(i.e.%20her%20recent%20social-media%20posts%20regarding%20the%20lawsuit)%20was%20harming%20the%20Hayley%20Paige%20business%2C%20as%20stores%20had%20stopped%20working%20with%20JLM%20after%20Gutman%20went%20public%20about%20the%20lawsuit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman's%20employment%20contract%20with%20JLM%20was%20valid%20through%20August%202022%2C%20and%20it%20included%20a%20non-compete%20clause%20that%20was%20valid%20for%20five%20years%20after%20her%20employment%20ended.%20In%20the%20memorandum%2C%20JLM%20argued%20Gutman's%20social-media%20activity%20at%20the%20time%20breached%20that%20clause%2C%20since%20it%20had%20led%20bridal%20stores%20to%20stop%20working%20with%20the%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20BI%20reached%20out%20to%20Gutman's%20team%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20memorandum%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20refuted%20JLM's%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM's%20latest%20claims%2C%20like%20their%20earlier%20ones%2C%20are%20full%20of%20assertions%20that%20are%20unsupported%20by%20the%20facts%20of%20the%20case%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20fail%20to%20address%20the%20evidence%20we%20presented%20to%20the%20Court%2C%20and%20we%20are%20looking%20forward%20to%20being%20heard.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hearing%20took%20place%20on%20February%204%2C%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20March%205%2C%202021%2C%20JLM%20was%20granted%20a%20preliminary%20injunction%20against%20Gutman.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%20gutman%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6047a0c244d8e300117b9d60%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJLM%20was%20granted%20a%20preliminary%20injunction.%3Cp%3ED%20Dipasupil%20%2F%20Contributor%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20month%20of%20deliberation%2C%20a%20judge%20ruled%20in%20JLM's%20favor%2C%20as%20stated%20in%20a%20JLM%20press%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJudge%20Swain%20found%20that%20JLM%20demonstrated%20a%20clear%20likelihood%20of%20success%20in%20proving%20Hayley%20Paige%20Gutman%20breached%20her%20employment%20contract%20and%20infringed%20the%20company's%20trademark%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20press%20release%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20prevented%20Gutman%20from%20using%20any%20%40misshayleypaige%20social-media%20accounts%20or%20Hayley%20Paige%20trademarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Murphy%20continues%20to%20recognize%20and%20value%20Ms.%20Gutman's%20talent%20and%20remains%20hopeful%20that%20JLM%20and%20Ms.%20Gutman%20can%20reconcile%20their%20differences%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20press%20release%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20ruling%20was%20a%20preliminary%20injunction%2C%20an%20additional%20hearing%20was%20held%20at%20a%20later%20date%20to%20examine%20the%20legal%20issues%20between%20JLM%20and%20Gutman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20disappointed%20in%20JLM's%20actions%20but%20determined%20to%20look%20to%20the%20future%20rather%20than%20the%20past%2C%26quot%3B%20Gutman%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20a%20statement%20regarding%20the%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20have%20taken%20my%20name%2C%20and%20my%20social%20media%20for%20now%2C%20but%20JLM's%20business%20is%20built%20on%20the%20goodwill%20of%20amazing%20women%2C%20and%20I%20believe%20they%20will%20be%20accountable%20to%20these%20women%20for%20what%20they%20have%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGutman%20announced%20she%20would%20be%20changing%20her%20professional%20name%20on%20Instagram%20on%20March%208%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60479ae144d8e300117b9d37%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20decided%20to%20change%20her%20professional%20name.%3Cp%3EInstagram%2Fallthatglittersonthegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%20to%20the%20lawsuit%2C%20Gutman%20announced%20on%20the%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%20Instagram%20account%20that%20she%20would%20be%20changing%20her%20name%20so%20she%20could%20continue%20to%20do%20business%20unassociated%20with%20JLM.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20may%20have%20lost%20this%20round%20in%20court%2C%20but%20the%20bigger%20story%20is%20about%20a%20'girl%20you%20might%20know%2C'%20who%20is%20determined%20to%20pave%20her%20own%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20Gutman%20said%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMKY9APH5EZ%2F%5C%22%3Ethe%20video%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BI%20refuse%20to%20be%20nameless%2C%20and%20I%20refuse%20to%20be%20jobless.%20Since%20they%20have%20taken%20my%20name%2C%20I've%20decided%20to%20change%20it%2C%20officially%20and%20professionally.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20be%20reduced%20by%20what%20has%20been%20taken%20from%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20had%20not%20picked%20her%20new%20professional%20name%20yet%2C%20and%20she%20asked%20her%20followers%20to%20help%20her%20choose%20a%20moniker%20in%20the%20video.%20She%20requested%20they%20choose%20a%20name%20that%20had%20zero%20association%20with%20her%20birth%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20to%20be%20brand%20new%2C%26quot%3B%20Gutman%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20can't%20be%20based%20off%20my%20birth%20name%20or%20anything%20I've%20done%20with%20JLM.%20They%20are%20a%20part%20of%20my%20past%2C%20and%20this%20is%20my%20future.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJLM%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20Gutman's%20decision%20to%20change%20her%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJLM%20posted%20a%20statement%20about%20the%20lawsuit%20on%20its%20corporate%20Instagram%20account%20on%20March%209%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jlm%20statement%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6047c30e44d8e300117b9e43%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJLM%20released%20a%20new%20statement.%3Cp%3EJLM%20Couture%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJLM%20Couture%20took%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCMMnxFdjuo1%2F%5C%22%3EInstagram%3C%2Fa%3E%20again%20on%20March%209%2C%202021%2C%20to%20make%20a%20general%20statement%20that%20addressed%20both%20the%20court%20ruling%20and%20Gutman's%20most%20recent%20video.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIntellectual%20property%20is%20the%20cornerstone%20of%20every%20modern%20business%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20fashion%20industry%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20read.%20%26quot%3BJLM%20takes%20these%20rights%20very%20seriously%2C%20which%20is%20why%20Ms.%20Gutman's%20employment%20agreement%20clearly%20and%20unambiguously%20set%20out%20Ms.%20Gutman's%20obligations%2C%20what%20rights%20were%20being%20acquired%20and%20what%20restrictions%20would%20be%20imposed%20on%20Ms.%20Gutman%2C%20all%20of%20which%20she%20freely%20and%20knowingly%20agreed%20to.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20JLM%20will%20never%20deny%20Ms.%20Gutman's%20talent%2C%20JLM%20rejects%20Ms.%20Gutman's%20accusations%20as%20well%20as%20her%20version%20of%20business%20ethics%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20went%20on%20to%20say.%20%26quot%3BMs.%20Gutman%20testified%20in%20court%20that%20she%20does%20not%20believe%20that%20a%20material%20omission%20is%20a%20form%20of%20a%20lie.%20JLM%20does%20not%20subscribe%20to%20that%20version%20of%20'business%20ethics'%20or%20how%20she%20is%20trying%20to%20mislead%20the%20public%20about%20the%20facts%20or%20the%20case%20or%20her%20own%20motivations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20her%20public%20statements%20Ms.%20Gutman%20omits%20the%20overwhelming%20evidence%20submitted%20to%20the%20court%20that%20these%20social%20media%20accounts%20were%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20Hayley%20Paige%20brand%20business%20and%20marketing%20strategy%2C%20and%20were%20run%20as%20such%2C%20including%20admissions%20to%20that%20effect%20in%20her%20own%20emails%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20also%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20Gutman%20hadn't%20told%20her%20followers%20that%20she%20had%20%26quot%3Bsecretly%20licensed%26quot%3B%20her%20name%20to%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%20so%20she%20could%20do%20business%20through%20him%20and%20avoid%20the%20terms%20of%20her%20contract.%20The%20statement%20also%20noted%20that%20Gutman%20used%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20accounts%20to%20promote%20Chosen%20Foods%20and%20Optimum%2C%20which%20violated%20her%20contract%20with%20JLM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM%20does%20not%20subscribe%20to%20her%20version%20of%20business%20ethics%20where%20consumers%20and%20followers%20are%20misled%20and%20not%20given%20the%20facts%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20court%20considered%20all%20of%20the%20actual%20evidence%20and%20facts%20in%20the%20case%2C%20it%20rejected%20her%20arguments.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM%20strongly%20encourages%20anyone%20interested%20in%20this%20case%20to%20read%20the%20court's%20entire%20decision%20and%20reach%20their%20own%20conclusions%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20a%20link%20to%20the%20court%20decision%20to%20the%20bio%20of%20its%20Instagram.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGutman%20responded%20to%20JLM's%20Instagram%20post%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider%20on%20March%209%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hpg%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6047d25b2db4af00117e460a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221499%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20responded%20to%20JLM%20via%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3Cp%3EInstagram%2Fallthatglittersonthegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20told%20Business%20Insider%20via%20email%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20changes%20in%20my%20life%20and%20moving%20forward%2C%26quot%3B%20when%20asked%20for%20comment%20on%20JLM's%20post.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20why%20I%20am%20changing%20my%20name.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM%20Couture%20is%20a%20company%20that%20relies%20entirely%20on%20women%20for%20its%20business%2C%20but%20it%20continues%20to%20treat%20women%20with%20utter%20disrespect%2C%26quot%3B%20Gutman%20went%20on%20to%20say.%20%26quot%3BJLM%20took%20control%20of%20my%20social%20media%20and%20never%20informed%20the%20followers%20of%20these%20accounts%20that%20they%20are%20speaking%20with%20a%20corporation%2C%20not%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM%20has%20also%20turned%20off%20comments%20on%20both%20my%20social%20media%20channels%20and%20their%20own%2C%20which%20is%20both%20deceptive%20and%20disrespectful%20to%20the%20thousands%20of%20strong%20women%20who%20have%20shared%20their%2