hat%20her%20team%20would%20be%20filing%20a%20response%20%26quot%3Bin%20due%20course.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM%20has%20concocted%20a%20series%20of%20harassing%20and%20false%20claims%20about%20both%20Conrad%20and%20Hayley%20with%20the%20clear%20intention%20of%20shutting%20down%20their%20ability%20to%20express%20their%20opinions%20about%20JLM%20and%20the%20merits%20of%20their%20litigation%2C%26quot%3B%20Gutman's%20representative%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20always%20felt%20that%20JLM%20was%20focused%20on%20controlling%20me%20personally%2C%20and%20this%20latest%20lawsuit%20is%20further%20evidence%20of%20that%2C%20and%20another%20reason%20why%20I%20resigned%E2%80%A6%20from%20a%20very%20hostile%20organization%2C%26quot%3B%20Gutman%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20disheartening%20to%20see%20them%20attempt%20to%20control%20what%20I%20can%20say%2C%20and%20even%20sadder%20to%20see%20them%20bring%20in%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%20to%20try%20to%20further%20hurt%20our%20lives%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGutman%20told%20her%20followers%20about%20JLM's%20lawsuit%20against%20herself%20and%20Clevlen%20via%20Instagram%20on%20May%204%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221470%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hayley%20Paige%20announces%20JLM%20is%20suing%20her%20fiance%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6092a7c434af8d001859b2d1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221102%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20made%20an%20Instagram%20video%20about%20the%20lawsuit.%3Cp%3EInstagram%2F%40allthatglittersonthegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20JLM%20was%20suing%20Gutman%20for%20defamation%20because%20of%20her%20Instagram%20videos%2C%20she%20posted%20a%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCOeRVkyHW4B%2F%5C%22%3E%C2%A0new%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20May%204%20%E2%80%94%20the%20anniversary%20of%20the%20day%20she%20