e%20to%20other%20videos%20she%20made%20regarding%20her%20legal%20issues%20with%20the%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM%20is%20now%20trying%20to%20charge%20me%20with%20defamation%20for%20my%20public%20videos%2C%20like%20the%20one%20you're%20watching%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20her%20followers.%20%26quot%3BThis%20has%20been%20my%20only%20legal%20outlet%20to%20let%20people%20know%20what%20has%20happened%2C%20and%20I%20will%20not%20be%20scared%20into%20staying%20quiet.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20with%20every%20single%20attempt%20JLM%20makes%20to%20muzzle%20me%20or%20drag%20down%20my%20loved%20ones%20and%20supporters%2C%20it%20only%20ignites%20greater%20purpose%20and%20meaning%20in%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Gutman%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20ended%20the%20video%20by%20saying%20her%20name%20and%20new%20brand%20were%20on%20their%20way%2C%20though%20she%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Bthere%20have%20been%20some%20pretty%20aggressive%20attempts%20to%20distract%26quot%3B%20her%20from%20launching%20a%20new%20bridal%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20will%20not%20allow%20pettiness%20and%20injustice%20to%20outrun%20my%20dreams%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EA%20representative%20for%20JLM%20denied%20Gutman's%20statements%20on%20Instagram%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221903%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22hayley%20paige%20lawsuit%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6092ed59f22c6b00185dc39c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221428%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJLM%20responded%20to%20Gutman%20via%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3Cp%3EInstagram%2F%40allthatglittersonthegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20JLM%20spokesperson%20rebuked%20a%20myriad%20of%20Gutman's%20claims%20to%20Business%20Insider%20on%20May%205%2C%20including%20her%20assertion%20that%20JLM%20is%20attempting%20to%20silence%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJ