3B%20to%20the%20company%2C%20and%20Gutman%20did%20not%20properly%20refute%20that%20claim.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMs.%20Gutman%20did%20not%20refute%20in%20her%20reply%2C%20or%20at%20oral%20argument%20respond%20meaningfully%20to%2C%20JLM's%20assertion%20of%20the%20Contract's%20conditional%20nature%2C%20at%20least%20with%20respect%20to%20base%20compensation%20and%20benefits%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20in%20her%20reply%20submission%2C%20Ms.%20Gutman%20simply%20asserted%20in%20conclusory%20fashion%20that%20there%20is%20'no%20question'%20that%20JLM's%20failure%20to%20pay%20her%20compensation%20and%20benefits%20is%20a%20material%20breach%20of%20the%20Contract.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20preliminary%20injunction%20was%20not%20dissolved%2C%20Gutman%20proceeded%20with%20an%20appeal%20of%20the%20ruling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGutman%20posted%20a%20video%20about%20the%20ruling%20on%20Instagram%20on%20June%207%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hayley%20Paige%20Gutman%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60bf9e1a93c6fa00195e5bce%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221499%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20appealed%20the%20preliminary%20injunction.%3Cp%3ESlaven%20Vlasic%20%2F%20Stringer%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20took%20to%20Instagram%20again%20on%20June%207%20to%20share%20an%20update%20with%20her%20followers%20on%20her%20legal%20proceedings%20with%20JLM.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCP0ixrinOEc%2F%5C%22%3Evideo%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20discussed%20the%20judge's%20denial%20to%20dissolve%20the%20preliminary%20injunction%20and%20said%20that%20JLM%20argued%20that%20it%20did%20not%20owe%20Gutman%20her%202020%20commission.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20also%20said%20that%20the%20company%20claimed%20she%20was%20paid%20commission%20