%20Insider.com%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMs.%20Gutman%20has%20refused%2C%20instead%20electing%20to%20further%20try%20to%20incite%20ill-will%20towards%20JLM%20Couture%2C%26quot%3B%20they%20went%20on%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM%20Couture%20will%20be%20seeking%20relief%20from%20the%20Court%20and%20will%20be%20filing%20a%20motion%20for%20contempt%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20July%2015%2C%202021%2C%20JLM%20officially%20filed%20a%20motion%20to%20hold%20Gutman%20in%20contempt%20of%20court.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20sits%20in%20a%20room%20with%20windows%20and%20looks%20off%20into%20the%20distance.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60f6f4121f6c450011ada531%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20motion%20was%20filed%20on%20July%2015.%3Cp%3EInstagram%2F%40allthatglittersonthegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJLM%20filed%20the%20motion%20and%20a%20memorandum%20of%20law%20to%20explain%20the%20motion%2C%20which%20Business%20Insider%20was%20able%20to%20review.%20The%20memo%20cited%20Gutman's%20social-media%20use%20and%20comments%20to%20the%20media%2C%20including%20Business%20Insider%2C%20as%20violations%20of%20the%20preliminary%20injunction%20issued%20against%20her%2C%20saying%20she%20was%20building%20a%20base%20of%20support%20for%20her%20new%20brand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20stated%20that%20%26quot%3BGutman's%20clear%20and%20admitted%20intent%20is%20to%20use%20the%20time%20the%20non-compete%20is%20in%20effect%20to%20market%20and%20promote%20the%20brand%2C%20build%20her%20consumer%20base%20and%20design%20her%20collection%2C%20so%20that%20her%20dresses%20can%20go%20on%20sale%20with%20a%20built-in%20customer%20base%20the%20day%20her%20non-compete%20ends%26quot%3B%20in%20August%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJLM's%20memo%20said%20the%20%40allthatglitter