20the%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%20Instagram%20were%20violations%20of%20the%20preliminary%20injunction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20stated%20that%20JLM%20sold%20her%20sketches%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Hayley%20Paige%20brand%20and%20used%20them%20for%20marketing%20purposes%2C%20so%20her%20posts%20violated%20the%20non-compete%20clause.%20It%20also%20said%20that%20a%20video%20she%20posted%20of%20herself%20drawing%20on%20June%2021%20included%20a%20sketch%20owned%20by%20JLM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20because%20Gutman%20did%20not%20remove%20the%20video%20about%20the%20new%20name%2C%20did%20not%20retract%20her%20statements%20to%20Business%20Insider%2C%20and%20continued%20to%20post%20videos%20of%20herself%20sketching%20to%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%2C%20JLM%20filed%20the%20motion%20of%20contempt.%20The%20company%20requested%20the%20court%20hold%20Gutman%20in%20civil%20contempt%20and%20order%20financial%20and%20equitable%20sanctions%20against%20her%20for%20the%20violations%20in%20the%20motion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJLM%20also%20wanted%20the%20court%20to%20require%20Gutman%20to%20remove%20three%20posts%20from%20the%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%20account%20and%20be%20%26quot%3Benjoined%26quot%3B%20from%20announcing%20her%20new%20name%20before%20the%20non-compete%20agreement%20expired.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGutman%20shared%20the%20news%20of%20the%20motion%20with%20her%20fans%20on%20the%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%20Instagram%20account%20on%20July%2020%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20sits%20in%20a%20room%20with%20windows%20and%20holds%20a%20hand%20to%20her%20chest.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F60f6f2a9b9172800127518fb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221499%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGutman%20discussed%20the%20motion%20of%20contempt%20on%20Instagram.%3Cp%3EInstagram%2F%40allthatglittersonthegram%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20continue%20to%20believe%20that%20this%20is%20just%20another%20attempt%20to%20prevent%20me%20from%20talking%20with%20you%20about%20this%20litigation%20and%20prevent%20me%20from%20shining%20any%20kind%20of%20light%20on%20what%20JLM%20is%20doing%2C%26quot%3B%20Gutman%20said%20in%20the%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20this%20point%2C%20seven%20grueling%20months%20into%20this%20dispute%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20nothing%20is%20enough%20for%20JLM%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20the%20video.%20%26quot%3BI%20feel%20like%20they%20just%20want%20me%20to%20sit%20down%20and%20shut%20up.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20also%20said%20in%20the%20video%20that%20JLM%20%26quot%3Bis%20now%20messaging%20people%20on%20Instagram%20and%20saying%20they've%20tried%20to%20settle%20with%20me%20many%20times%20and%20that%20I%20refuse%20to%20engage%20in%20settlement.%26quot%3B%20She%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20was%20false%20and%20that%20she%20remained%20%26quot%3Bvery%20open%20and%20willing%20to%20solve%20this%20dispute%20in%20a%20professional%20and%20business-oriented%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20adding%20that%20she%20had%20made%20a%20settlement%20proposal%20while%20JLM%20had%20not.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20ill-considered%20effort%20by%20JLM%20to%20try%20to%20control%20public%20conversation%20about%20their%20poor%20decisions%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20representative%20for%20Gutman%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BJLM%20continues%20to%20prohibit%20most%20public%20comment%20on%20the%20various%20social%20media%20channels%20they%20control%2C%20and%20has%20gone%20so%20far%20as%20to%20delete%20prior%20negative%20comments%20about%20their%20actions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20combination%20with%20this%20latest%20effort%20to%20use%20the%20courts%20to%20avoid%20public%20opinion%2C%20it's%20clear%20that%20JLM%20is%20suffering%20great%20harm%20from%20the%20litigation%20they%20started.%20They%20have%20no%20one%20but%20themselves%20to%20blame%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20representative%20went%20on%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJLM%20reiterated%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20motion%20for%20contempt%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJLM%20Couture%20Inc.%20was%20forced%20on%20July%2015%20to%20seek%20relief%20in%20Federal%20Court%20after%20Ms.%20Gutman's%20continuous%20flagrant%20violations%20of%20Judge%20Laura%20Taylor%20Swain's%20order%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20JLM%20said.%20%26quot%3BMs.%20Gutman%20was%20asked%20to%20stop%20violating%20Judge%20Swain's%20order%20and%20to%20take%20down%20the%20infringing%20videos%20and%20posts%20%E2%80%93%20but%20she%20refused.%20This%20left%20JLM%20Couture%20no%20choice%20but%20to%20seek%20immediate%20relief%20from%20the%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMs.%20Gutman's%20video%20released%20this%20morning%20continues%20to%20promote%20a%20false%20and%20misleading%20narrative%20with%20reference%20to%20the%20contempt%20motion%20itself%20and%20the%20interactions%20between%20the%20parties%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20went%20on%20to%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGutman%20said%20JLM's%20actions%20didn't%20%26quot%3Bsurprise%26quot%3B%20her%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20does%20not%20surprise%20me%20that%20JLM%20continues%20to%20blame%20me%20instead%20of%20acknowledging%20the%20impact%20of%20its%20own%20actions%3B%20and%20that%20JLM%20continues%20to%20want%20to%20silence%20and%20restrain%20me%20instead%20of%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20move%20forward%20in%20a%20professional%2C%20business-minded%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20contempt%20motion's%20vitriol%20speaks%20for%20itself.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGutman%20was%20held%20in%20contempt%20of%20court%20on%20September%208%2C%202021.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hayley%20Paige%20Gutman%20wears%20a%20black%20hat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F613a6657a30aeb0018b4ca56%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20judge%20found%20Gutman%20was%20in%20contempt%20of%20court.%3Cp%3EEugene%20Gologursky%20%2F%20Contributor%20%2F%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJLM's%20request%20to%20hold%20Gutman%20in%20contempt%20was%20partially%20granted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20stated%20in%20a%20memorandum%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20the%20court%20found%20that%20Gutman%20was%20marketing%20her%20upcoming%20brand%20with%20her%20posts%20and%20comments%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20Because%20her%20future%20brand%20would%20directly%20compete%20with%20JLM%2C%20it%20was%20ruled%20that%20Gutman's%20posts%20and%20comments%20put%20her%20in%20willful%2C%20civil%20contempt%20of%20the%20preliminary%20injunction%20issued%20in%20March.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Csection%3E%3C%2Fsection%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20decided%20that%20Gutman%20was%20enjoined%20from%20%26quot%3Bannouncing%20a%20new%20brand%20name%20in%20the%20context%20of%20a%20present%20or%20future%20commercial%20venture%20involving%26quot%3B%20bridal%20wear%2C%20bridal%20accessories%2C%20evening%20wear%2C%20or%20any%20other%20products%20sold%20by%20JLM%20until%20the%20preliminary%20injunction%20expired%20in%20August%20of%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20memorandum%2C%20Gutman%20would%20have%20to%20pay%20JLM's%20%26quot%3Breasonable%20attorneys'%20fees%20and%20costs%26quot%3B%20because%20she%20violated%20the%20terms%20of%20the%20preliminary%20injunction.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20also%20ordered%20to%20delete%20Instagram%20posts%20from%20the%20%40allthatglittersonthegram%20post%20related%20to%20her%20plans%20for%20a%20new%20brand%20from%20May%207%2C%20June%207%2C%20June%2021%2C%20June%2025%2C%20and%20July%2015%2C%202021%2C%20within%20five%20days%20of%20the%20ruling%2C%20as%20stated%20in%20the%20memorandum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGutman%20shared%20the%20news%20on%20the%20%40allthatgli