asn't%20really%20seeing%20litigation%20as%20a%20place%20where%20there%20were%20going%20to%20be%20winners%20and%20losers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20saw%20it%20as%20almost%20like%20an%20infinite%20game.%20So%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'I%20need%20to%20choose%20a%20new%20path.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Apil%2030%2C%20JLM%20objected%20to%20the%20motion%20in%20a%20separate%20filing%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Motion%20should%20be%20denied%20as%20a%20transparent%20effort%20by%20a%20former%20employee%20to%20push%20her%20own%20agenda%20of%20destroying%20the%20Debtor%20to%20the%20detriment%20of%20the%20best%20interests%20of%20all%20creditors%2C%26quot%3B%20its%20filing%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOn%20May%208%2C%20the%20New%20York%20District%20Court%20ordered%20JLM%20to%20reinstate%20Gutman's%20access%20to%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20social-media%20accounts.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hayley%20Paige%20sits%20on%20a%20pink%20ottoman%20wearing%20fluffy%20shoes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66561ff3a961b37edf3a74bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222249%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20District%20Court%20modified%20its%20ruling.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Hayley%20Paige%20Gutman%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20memorandum%20reviewed%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20the%20New%20York%20District%20Court%20dissolved%20and%20modified%20sections%20of%20the%20preliminary%20injunction%20modification%20JLM%20was%20granted%20against%20Gutman%20in%20March%202023.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memorandum%20stated%20that%20%26quot%3BJLM%20has%20failed%20to%20carry%20its%20burden%20of%20demonstrating%20a%20clear%20or%20substantial%20likelihood%20of%20success%20in%20establishing%20that%20it%20was%20the%20original%20owner%20or%20transferee%20of%26quot%3B%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20accounts%20using%20the%20Second%20Circuit's%20legal%20framework%2C%20so%20its%20request%20to%20control%20Gutman's%20access%20to%20the%20accounts%20was%20not%20legally%20sound.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memorandum%20ordered%20JLM%20to%20restore%20Gutman's%20access%20to%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20accounts%20by%20May%2015.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJLM%20and%20Gutman%20reached%20a%20settlement%20agreement%20on%20May%2014%2C%20giving%20Gutman%20her%20name%20and%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20social-media%20accounts.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221721%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20blond%20woman%20stands%20in%20a%20cobblestone%20street%20in%20a%20blue%2C%20sparkly%20dress.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6656201320abc1efe8fe25b3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221290%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJLM%20and%20Hayley%20Paige%20Gutman%20reached%20a%20settlement%20agreement.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Pauline%20Photography%2FCourtesy%20of%20Hayley%20Paige%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reviewed%20the%20agreement%2C%20which%20was%20between%20Gutman%2C%20Conrad%20Clevlen%2C%20JLM%2C%20and%20Joe%20Murphy.%20The%20bankruptcy%20court%20approved%20the%20agreement%20on%20Friday.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbridal-designer-hayley-paige-jlm-couture-reach-settlement-2024-5%5C%22%3Egave%20Gutman%20ownership%20of%20all%20intellectual%20property%20associated%20with%20Hayley%20Paige%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20her%20name%2C%20the%20%40misshayleypaige%20social-media%20pages%2C%20her%20designs%2C%20sketches%2C%20and%20past%20lookbooks.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agreement%20also%20released%20Gutman%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20all%20rights%2C%20restrictions%2C%20and%2For%20obligations%20to%20JLM%2C%26quot%3B%20including%20her%20noncompete%20agreement%2C%20so%20she%20can%20design%20wedding%20gowns%20under%20her%20name.%20Gutman%20also%20told%20BI%20she%20will%20keep%20designing%20shoes%20under%