20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnyone%20born%20before%20the%20advent%20of%20the%20digital%20age%20likely%20has%20a%20big%20box%20of%20family%20photos%20sitting%20somewhere%20in%20their%20home%3B%20a%20relic%20of%20the%20days%20before%20smartphones%20replaced%20analog%20cameras%20and%20the%20cloud%20replaced%20film%20prints.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%2C%20too%2C%20have%20such%20a%20box%20and%20have%20made%20various%20attempts%20over%20the%20years%20to%20digitize%20the%20photos%20so%20they%20can%20be%20safely%20preserved%20and%20easily%20sorted%20in%20my%20Google%20Drive.%20Unfortunately%2C%20without%20specialized%20equipment%2C%20photo%20scanning%20is%20a%20time-consuming%20process%2C%20and%20while%20phone%20apps%20like%20Photomyne%20aim%20to%20make%20the%20process%20faster%2C%20I've%20found%20the%20quality%20of%20the%20scans%20is%20often%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20too%20bothered%20by%20my%20lack%20of%20progress%20on%20my%20photo%20scanning%20project%20until%20I%20came%20across%20my%2090-year-old%20grandmother's%20trove%20of%20family%20photos%20last%20summer.%20Contained%20within%20five%20huge%20boxes%20were%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20photographs%20representing%20over%20a%20century%20of%20family%20history.%20Many%20of%20the%20photos%20and%20albums%20had%20already%20been%20damaged%20by%20basement%20flooding%20or%20faded%20with%20time%2C%20so%20it%20suddenly%20became%20imperative%20that%20I%20find%20a%20way%20to%20quickly%20digitize%20this%20massive%20cache%20of%20photos%20so%20future%20generations%20could%20enjoy%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEnter%20the%20Epson%20FastFoto%20(FF-680W)%2C%20the%20only%20home%20scanner%20on%20the%20market%20that%20can%20batch-process%20up%20to%2035%20photos%20at%20a%20time%2C%20with%20scanning%20speeds%20up%20to%2080%20photos%20per%20minute.%20Overall%2C%20I%20think%20this%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20and%20most%20economical%20solutions%20for%20anyone%20who%20has%20a%20lot%20of%20photos%20to%20scan%2C%20but%20once%20your%20project%20is%20complete%2C%20you%20may%20find%20little%20use%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%5C%22%3EAn%20upright%20scanner%20that%20takes%20up%20little%20desk%20space%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20size%20comparison%20of%20the%20Epson%20FastFoto%20next%20to%20a%20standard%20home%20printer%2C%20showing%20the%20FastFoto%20is%20significantly%20smaller%20than%20the%20printer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65a835106979d737182418b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Epson%20FastFoto%20(left)%2C%20is%20quite%20a%20bit%20smaller%20than%20my%20HP%20OfficeJet%20(right).%20While%20the%20OfficeJet%20has%20can%20scan%20images%2C%20it%20is%20much%20slower%20and%20more%20manual%20process%20than%20with%20the%20FastFoto.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FastFoto%20looks%20like%20a%20shrunken-down%20version%20of%20a%20classic%20printer%20and%20fits%20easily%20on%20a%20desk%20for%20easy%20access.%20Make%20no%20mistake%3A%20The%20FastFoto%20%3Cem%3Eonly%3C%2Fem%3E%20scans%20and%20has%20no%20printing%20functions.%20And%2C%20this%20scanner%20is%20primarily%20designed%20for%20digitizing%20printed%20photos%20with%20a%20maximum%20width%20and%20height%20of%208.5%20inches%20by%2011.7%20inches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20put%20the%20photos%20into%20the%20scanner%20like%20you%20would%20load%20paper%20into%20a%20printer%3A%20there's%20a%20feeder%20with%20sliders%20to%20accommodate%20various%20picture%20sizes.%20The%20photos%20are%20pulled%20through%20the%20scanner%20and%20deposited%20in%20the%20landing%20tray.%20The%20whole%20unit%20has%20a%20cover%20that%20protects%20the%20scanner%20from%20dust%20when%20not%20in%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20a%20traditional%20flatbed%20scanner%2C%20where%20you%20lift%20a%20cover%20and%20scan%20each%20one%20at%20a%20time%2C%20the%20feeder%20system%20speeds%20up%20the%20process%20and%20makes%20photo-scanning%20and%20archiving%20more%20convenient.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20the%20FastFoto%20resembles%20Epson's%20other%20sheet-fed%20document%20scanners%2C%20it's%20not%20designed%20for%20multi-page%20document%20scanning.%20I've%20tried%2C%20but%20since%20it%20scans%20each%20page%20as%20an%20individual%20file%2C%20you're%20forced%20to%20assemble%20the%20PDF%20manually.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Setup%2C%20controls%2C%20and%20connectivity%5C%22%3ESimple%20setup%2C%20controls%2C%20and%20connectivity%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20have%20two%20options%20for%20connecting%20the%20FastFoto%20to%20your%20computer%3A%20use%20the%20included%20USB-A%20or%20connect%20via%20WiFi.%20Like%20many%20current%20laptops%2C%20my%20computer%20has%20no%20USB-A%20slots%2C%20so%20I%20used%20WiFi.%20The%20scanner%20is%20outfitted%20to%20connect%20to%20WiFi%20via%20your%20router's%20WPS%20button%2C%20which%20simplifies%20the%20wireless%20pairing.%20If%20your%20router%20has%20no%20WPS%20button%2C%20you%20can%20manually%20connect%20your%20scanner%20to%20the%20network%20using%20Epson's%20scanning%20software%20or%20smartphone%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Scanning%20and%20photo%20quality%5C%22%3ELightning-fast%2C%20high-quality%20scans%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEpson%20suggests%20that%20you%20organize%20your%20photos%20by%20size%20and%20orientation%20before%20scanning.%20This%20was%20by%20far%20the%20most%20time-consuming%20process.%20I%20took%20it%20a%20step%20further%20and%20also%20organized%20photos%20by%20year.%20The%20software%20allows%20you%20to%20set%20a%20date%20for%20each%20batch%20of%20photos%20you%20scan.%20While%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20use%20this%20feature%2C%20this%20step%20is%20important%20if%20you%20plan%20on%20importing%20your%20scans%20into%20an%20app%20like%20Google%20Photos%20and%20want%20to%20have%20your%20scanned%20images%20accurately%20organized%20by%20year.%20Organizing%20my%20photos%20this%20way%20took%20about%204%20hours%20for%201%2C800%20images.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20show%20stacks%20of%20photos%20on%20a%20desk%20next%20to%20the%20photos%20neatly%20organized%20by%20year%20in%20a%20box%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aea71bdcdb354a9859b3f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20started%20organizing%20my%20photos%20by%20size%20and%20orientation%20(left)%20and%20then%20grouped%20everything%20by%20year%20(right).%20This%20is%20recommended%20by%20Epson%20to%20make%20scanning%20go%20faster.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20had%20my%20images%20organized%2C%20the%20actual%20process%20of%20scanning%20took%20barely%20an%20hour.%20I%20was%20shocked%20that%20in%20such%20a%20short%20period%2C%20I%20had%20tackled%20a%20huge%20project%20that%20had%20daunted%20me%20for%20years.%20The%20one-hour%20scanning%20time%20included%20dealing%20with%20a%20few%20snags%20and%20re-scans%20(I'll%20explain%20a%20bit%20more%20about%20that%20below)%2C%20loading%20and%20unloading%20the%20photos%2C%20and%20changing%20the%20date%20within%20the%20Epson%20software%20for%20each%20new%20batch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20scanning%2C%20the%20software%20deposits%20the%20images%20into%20folders%20on%20your%20computer%20organized%20by%20year.%20For%20each%20image%2C%20the%20software%20creates%20two%20to%20three%20files%3A%20an%20original%2C%20an%20enhanced%20version%2C%20and%20a%20scan%20of%20the%20back%20of%20the%20photo%20if%20any%20images%20or%20text%20were%20detected.%20This%20last%20feature%20was%20both%20a%20blessing%20and%20a%20curse%3A%20I%20loved%20that%20it%20automatically%20preserved%20the%20hand-written%20notes%20on%20many%20of%20my%20grandma's%20photos%2C%20but%20I%20also%20ended%20up%20with%20many%20images%20of%20blank%20photo%20backs%20because%20the%20scanner%20had%20detected%20a%20logo%20on%20the%20photo%20paper%20commonly%20used%20to%20print%20film%20back%20in%20the%20analog%20days.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20showing%20a%20photo%20of%20an%20old%20man%20with%20original%20coloring%20and%20with%20the%20enhanced%20coloring%20from%20the%20Epson%20FastFoto%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aff93a6c8f0a134f793bdf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20FastFoto%20creates%20both%20an%20original%20and%20enhanced%20file%20for%20each%20scan%2C%20as%20shown%20here%20with%20one%20of%20my%20photos.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20most%20cases%2C%20I%20actually%20preferred%20the%20enhanced%20version%20of%20the%20image.%20I%20thought%20the%20software%20did%20a%20good%20job%20of%20color-correcting%20and%20clarifying%20images%20so%20more%20detail%20was%20visible.%20None%20of%20the%20scans%20had%20glare%2C%20blur%2C%20or%20pixelation%2C%20which%20are%20issues%20I've%20encountered%20with%20phone%20scanning%20apps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20showing%20the%20same%20photo%20scanned%20with%20a%20cellphone%20app%20and%20with%20the%20Epson%20FastFoto%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65aff698617029e90a5f9645%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20same%20photo%2C%20as%20scanned%20by%20a%20cellphone%20app%20and%20the%20Epson%20FastFoto.%20The%20FastFoto%20scan%20has%20clearer%20picture%20quality%2C%20brighter%20colors%2C%20and%20no%20glare.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20I%20thought%20the%20scanner%20did%20a%20phenomenal%20job%20scanning%20standard%20photo%20sizes%3A%204%20x%206%20and%205%20x%207%20inches.%20I%20encountered%20more%20difficulty%20with%20atypical%20sizes%2C%20thicknesses%2C%20or%20materials%20(like%20Polaroid%20photos).%20Scanning%20these%20requires%20using%20the%20FastFoto's%20included%20carrier%20sheet.%20I%20thought%20this%20sheet%20introduced%20some%20color%20distortion%20and%20a%20ripple%20effect%20where%20the%20transparency%20covers%20the%20photo.%20Once%20these%20photos%20were%20scanned%2C%20they%20had%20to%20be%20manually%20cropped%20and%20rotated%3B%20a%20task%20I%20found%20a%20bit%20tedious.%20Fortunately%2C%20atypical%20photos%20only%20made%20up%20a%20small%20fraction%20of%20all%20the%20images%20I%20needed%20to%20scan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20pain%20point%20was%20that%20several%20times%20during%20scanning%2C%20the%20FastFoto%20stopped%20mid-scan%2C%20and%20I'd%20get%20a%20spinning%20wheel%20on%20the%20software%20screen.%20When%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20the%20issue%20wouldn't%20resolve%20on%20its%20own%2C%20I%20had%20to%20force%20quit%20the%20software%20or%20restart%20the%20scanner.%20Both%20these%20actions%20caused%20me%20to%20lose%20every%20photo%20I%20had%20already%20scanned%20in%20the%20current%20batch%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20hundreds%20of%20photos.%20It%20also%20forced%20me%20to%20retrieve%20the%20stuck%20photo%20from%20the%20grip%20of%20the%20scanner%20belts%2C%20which%20ruined%20at%20least%20one%20of%20my%20photos.%20This%20inexplicable%20shutdown%20happened%20three%20times%20during%20the%20course%20of%20my%20project.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221926%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22screenshot%20of%20Epson%20FastFoto%20software%20with%20Skitch%20arrows%20pointing%20to%20various%20errors%20in%20the%20photo%20scans.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65b7d6d243bb77284ba1524d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221444%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20screenshot%20shows%20the%20main%20page%20of%20the%20FastFoto%20scanning%20app.%20Despite%20its%20speedy%20scanning%2C%20I%20still%20needed%20to%20make%20some%20manual%20adjustments%20to%20the%20photos%2C%20including%20cropping%20and%20rotating.%3Cp%3ELauren%20Savoie%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20the%20purported%20integration%20with%20Google%20Photos%20failed%20for%20me.%20%C2%A0I%20had%20to%20upload%20all%20my%20images%20to%20Google%20Photos%20manually.%20Again%2C%20this%20only%20took%20a%20few%20extra%20steps%2C%20but%20is%20another%20frustrating%20glitch%20in%20the%20buggy%20and%20dated-feeling%20software.%20I'm%20no%20software%20engineer%2C%20but%20I%20think%20there%20could%20be%20vast%20improvements%20to%20user%20experience%20with%20just%20a%20few%20simple%20updates%20to%20the%20app.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Should%20you%20buy%20the%20Epson%20FastFoto%3F%5C%22%3EShould%20you%20buy%20the%20Epson%20FastFoto%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20deny%20that%20this%20scanner%20quickly%20loses%20its%20utility%20after%20completing%20your%20project%2C%20which%20took%20only%20a%20few%20days%20for%20me.%20Since%20it%20can't%20print%20and%20isn't%20ideal%20for%20document%20scanning%20(my%20printer%20is%20more%20user-friendly%20for%20scanning%20multi-page%20text%20documents)%2C%20you%20basically%20just%20have%20a%20bulky%2C%20pricey%20electronic%20with%20little%20use%20on%20your%20hands.%20You%20can%20sell%20it%20or%20loan%20it%20out%20to%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20but%20in%20this%20digital%20age%2C%20there%20aren't%20many%20circumstances%20where%20you'll%20accumulate%20a%20cache%20of%20analog%20photos%20that%20need%20scanning%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20from%20my%20research%2C%20the%20alternatives%20to%20the%20Epson%20FastFoto%20boil%20down%20to%20three%20options%3A%20hire%20a%20service%20(pricey)%2C%20scan%20the%20photos%20manually%20(time-consuming)%2C%20or%20use%20a%20phone%20app%20(low%20quality).%20The%20going%20rate%20for%20professional%20photo%20scanning%20is%20about%20%240.17%20per%20photo%2C%20so%20I'd%20say%20that%20if%20you%20have%20more%20than%203%2C000%20photos%20to%20scan%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20FastFoto%20is%20well%20justified.%20You'll%20just%20need%20to%20plan%20for%20what%20to%20do%20with%20it%20when%20your%20project%20has%20wrapped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20bottom%20line%5C%22%3EThe%20bottom%20line%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Epson%20FastFoto%20is%20the%20easiest%20and%20fastest%20solution%20I've%20found%20for%20digitizing%20old%20photos.%20It's%20a%20load%20off%20my%20shoulders%20to%20know%20that%20my%20precious%20family%20memories%20are%20preserved%20and%20backed%20up%20digitally%20in%20case%20anything%20ever%20happens%20to%20the%20originals.%20If%20you%20have%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20photos%20to%20scan%2C%20this%20is%20far%20and%20away%20the%20best%20value%20solution%2C%20and%20one%20I%20highly%20recommend%20for%20peace%20of%20mind%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20preserving%20important%20family%20mementos.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fepson-fastfoto-ff680w-photo-scanner-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716935401000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665657d885e29ef64829aebc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fepson-fastfoto-ff680w-photo-scanner-review%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Epson%20FastFoto%20is%20an%20impressive%20scanner%20designed%20for%20digitizing%20printed%20photos%20easily%20and%20quickly%2C%20but%20it%20may%20not%20have%20much%20use%20outside%20that.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lsavoie%40insider.com%20(Lauren%20Savoie)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A50%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fepson-fastfoto-ff680w-photo-scanner-review%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Melinda%20French%20Gates%20to%20donate%20%241bn%20in%2