D%5C%22Former%20presidential%20candidate%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20addresses%20the%20media%20outside%20of%20Manhattan%20Criminal%20Court%20on%20behalf%20of%20former%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20May%2014%2C%202024%20in%20New%20York%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66564a5920abc1efe8fe53cd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVivek%20Ramaswamy%20has%20been%20buying%20up%20shares%20of%20BuzzFeed.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Dee%20Delgado%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EInvestor%20and%20former%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%C2%A0Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20has%20laid%20out%20his%20plans%20for%20BuzzFeed.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20envisions%20turning%20the%20company%20into%20a%20Twitter%2FX-style%20user-generated%20content%20company.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20BuzzFeed%20CEO%20Jonah%20Peretti%20controls%20the%20company%2C%20and%20doesn't%20take%C2%A0Ramaswamy%20seriously.%20So%20what's%20the%20endgame%20here%3F%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Republican%20presidential%20candidate%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20announced%20last%20week%20he%20had%20been%20buying%20up%20shares%20in%20BuzzFeed.%20Which%20led%20to%20the%20obvious%20question%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvivek-ramaswamy-buzzfeed-theories-why-buying-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWhy%20is%20Vivek%20Ramaswamy%20buying%20up%20shares%20in%20BuzzFeed%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20we%20know.%20Sort%20of.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERamaswamy%20says%20he%20has%20been%20buying%20up%20shares%20in%20BuzzFeed%20%E2%80%94%20he%20says%20he%20now%20owns%208.37%25%20of%20the%20company's%20%26quot%3BA%26quot%3B%20shares%20%E2%80%94%20because%20he%20has%20a%20plan%20to%20turn%20the%20struggling%20publisher%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20laid%20it%20out%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FVivekGRamaswamy%2Fstatus%2F1795446104781168827%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eletter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20BuzzFeed's%20board%2C%20but%20if%20you're%20in%20a%20hurry%20I%20can%20summarize%20it%20for%20you%3A%20Ramaswamy%20wants%20BuzzFeed%20to%20pull%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EElon%20Musk%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20is%3A%20He%20wants%20the%20company%20to%20cut%20costs%20to%20the%20bone%2C%20sell%20off%20some%20of%20its%20remaining%20assets%2C%20and%20transform%20itself%20into%20an%20X-style%20(that%20is%2C%20the%20company%20formerly%20known%20as%20Twitter%20since%20Musk%20bought%20it)%20video%20and%20audio%20platform%20%E2%80%94%20one%20that's%20particularly%20appealing%20to%20commentators%20from%20%26quot%3BTucker%20Carlson%20to%20Bill%20Maher%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20his%20letter.%20He%20says%20the%20first%20step%20would%20be%20to%20elect%20three%20Ramaswamy-endorsed%20board%20members%20in%20July.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20more%20in%20the%20letter%20if%20you%20want%20to%20get%20into%20it.%20For%20instance%2C%20Ramaswamy%20spends%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20lambasting%20BuzzFeed%20for%20things%20the%20company%20has%20published%20in%20the%20past%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.buzzfeednews.com%2Farticle%2Fkenbensinger%2Fthese-reports-allege-trump-has-deep-ties-to-russia%23.fiq8pA6W%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump%20%26quot%3Bdossier.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20And%20he%20wants%20BuzzFeed%20to%20apologize%2C%20because%20%26quot%3Bby%20both%20omission%20and%20commission%2C%20%5Bit%5D%20repeatedly%20lied%20on%20issues%20of%20national%20importance%2C%20and%20so%20did%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20media%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20writes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20you%20wanted%20to%20take%20this%20stuff%20at%20face%20value%2C%20you%20might%20also%20note%20that%20some%20things%20Ramaswamy%20is%20pushing%20for%20sound%20like%20things%20BuzzFeed%20CEO%20and%20founder%20Jonah%20Peretti%20has%20said%20he%20wants%20to%20do%20%E2%80%94%20notably%20the%20idea%20of%20using%20the%20company%20as%20a%20creator-friendly%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20I%20don't%20think%20that's%20a%20particularly%20useful%20way%20to%20spend%20your%20time.%20Debating%20the%20merits%20of%20Ramaswamy's%20plan%20seems%20like%20a%20cart-horse%20problem%20since%20Peretti%20has%20control%20of%20the%20company%20via%20a%20dual-class%20share%20structure%2C%20which%20gives%20him%2064%25%20of%20the%20company's%20voting%20rights.%20That's%20a%20structure%20specifically%20set%20up%20to%20give%20Peretti%20the%20ability%20to%20fend%20off%20takeovers%20or%20activist%20investors%20like%20Ramaswamy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20Peretti%20does%20not%20seem%20like%20he's%20treating%20Ramaswamy%20seriously.%20Here's%20the%20relevant%20part%20of%20his%20response%20to%20Ramaswamy's%20letter%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cblockquote%3E%3Csection%3EBased%20on%20your%20letter%2C%20you%20have%20some%20fundamental%20misunderstandings%20about%20the%20drivers%20of%20our%20business%2C%20the%20values%20of%20our%20audience%2C%20and%20the%20mission%20of%20the%20company.%20I'm%20very%20skeptical%20it%20makes%20business%20sense%20to%20turn%20BuzzFeed%20into%20a%20creator%20platform%20for%20inflammatory%20political%20pundits.%20And%20we're%20definitely%20not%20going%20to%20issue%20an%20apology%20for%20our%20Pulitzer%20Prize-winning%20journalism.%3C%2Fsection%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20unless%20Ramaswamy%20has%20another%20card%20to%20play%2C%20I%20still%20don't%20understand%20what%20his%20end%20goal%20is%20here.%20(I%20have%20asked%20him%20for%20comment.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20previously%20speculated%20that%20this%20was%20a%20relatively%20cheap%20way%20for%20Ramaswamy%20to%20keep%20his%20name%20in%20the%20news%2C%20and%20to%20court%20an%20audience%20receptive%20to%20Donald%20Trump's%20grievance%20politics.%20So%20maybe%20that's%20still%20the%20main%20driver%20here.%20Though%20it's%20hard%20to%20believe%20there's%20deep%20interest%20from%20MAGA-land%20about%20the%20state%20of%20BuzzFeed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20option%20would%20be%20for%20Ramaswamy%20to%20play%20this%20out%20a%20while%20longer%20and%20watch%20BuzzFeed%20shares%20shoot%20up%20based%20on%20his%20saber-rattling.%20BuzzFeed%20shares%20closed%20at%20%243%20today%2C%20up%2020%25%20from%20May%2022%2C%20when%20Ramaswamy%20first%20disclosed%20his%20stake.%20If%20it%20keeps%20heading%20up%2C%20it%20might%20be%20tempting%20for%20Ramaswamy%20to%20sell%20off%20his%20shares%2C%20and%20then%20simply%20declare%20that%20he's%20decided%20it's%20cheaper%20to%20build%20his%20own%20platform.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuzzfeed-vivek-ramawsamy-letter-jonah-peretti-2024-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716933304000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6656508585e29ef64829aca7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuzzfeed-vivek-ramawsamy-letter-jonah-peretti-2024-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sure%2C%20he%20could%20turn%20BuzzFeed%20into%20a%20mini%20version%20of%20Elon%20Musk's%20Twitter.%20But%20the%20guy%20who%20controls%20BuzzFeed%20wants%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20that.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pkafka%40insider.com%20(Peter%20Kafka)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuzzfeed-vivek-ramawsamy-letter-jonah-peretti-2024-5%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Jim%20Henson%20Idea%20Man%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20A%20Heartfelt%2C%20If%20Safe%2C%20Tribute%20to%20a%20Singular%20Figure%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716933196000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2F0410new_v3-0013_jmhnsnidmn_ov_v30444094_tb_dto_prohq_uh_74a0cf3f.jpeg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236017398%22%2C%22summary