20try%20out%20for%20months%20risk-free%20before%20committing%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESetup%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20you%20don't%20get%20an%20in-home%20setup%2C%20you%20want%20the%20unboxing%20to%20be%20as%20effortless%20as%20possible.%20I%20time%20how%20long%20it%20takes%20me%20to%20set%20up%20a%20mattress%20and%20note%20any%20strange%20or%20confusing%20steps.%20Most%20take%20less%20than%20five%20minutes.%20I%20also%20take%20a%20good%20whiff%20to%20see%20if%20there%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bnew%20bed%20smell%26quot%3B%20and%20check%20again%20before%20going%20to%20bed%20(at%20least%2010%20hours%20later)%20to%20see%20if%20the%20odor%20has%20dissipated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMotion%20isolation%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20A%20partner's%20tossing%20and%20turning%20can%20wake%20you%20up%20at%20night%2C%20so%20finding%20a%20mattress%20in%20a%20box%20with%20good%20motion%20isolation%20is%20important.%20In%20addition%20to%20tracking%20my%20subjective%20experience%2C%20I%20perform%20an%20objective%20test%20where%20I%20drop%20a%2015-pound%20bowling%20ball%20onto%20the%20mattress%20from%20a%20height%20of%204%20feet%20so%20that%20it%20lands%2012%20inches%20from%20a%2012-ounce%20can%20of%20soda%20pop.%20If%20the%20can%20stays%20upright%2C%20the%20bed%20has%20good%20motion%20isolation.%20If%20it%20doesn't%2C%20the%20motion%20isolation%20is%20poor.%20I%20also%20place%20a%20vibrometer%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20bed%20to%20measure%20the%20vibrations%20produced%20by%20the%20bowling%20ball.%20The%20less%20intense%20the%20vibrations%2C%20the%20better%20the%20motion%20isolation%20is.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22raw%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fgiphy.com%2Fembed%2Fp58rY8xCKaDzURD9Ti%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEdge%20support%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20is%20a%20somewhat%20subjective%20test.%20I%20lie%20on%20the%20very%20edge%20of%20the%20bed%20and%20slowly%20roll%20until%20I%20literally%20fall.%20I%20note%20how%20much%20I%20can%20roll%20before%20I%20fall.%20I%20also%20sit%20on%20the%20side%20of%20the%20bed%2C%20put%20on%20my%20shoes%20and%20socks%2C%20and%20observe%20how%20much%20the%20mattress%20sinks.%20When%20sleeping%20on%20the%20bed%2C%20I%20pay%20attention%20to%20how%20I%20feel%20close%20to%20the%20edges%20and%20if%20it%20feels%20like%20I'm%20going%20to%20fall%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPortability%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20We%20don't%20weigh%20portability%20heavily%2C%20but%20it's%20useful%20to%20know%20how%20easy%20a%20mattress%20is%20to%20move%20around%20if%20you%20frequently%20redecorate%20or%20relocate%2C%20regularly%20rotate%20your%20bed%20to%20increase%20its%20longevity%2C%20or%20need%20to%20reposition%20it%20to%20put%20on%20fitted%20sheets.%20I%20move%20each%20mattress%20around%20several%20times%20during%20testing%20and%20note%20if%20it%20flops%20around%2C%20has%20handles%2C%20or%20is%20generally%20hard%20to%20move.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20more%20details%2C%20check%20out%20our%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-we-test-mattresses%5C%22%3Ehow%20we%20test%20mattresses%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22FAQs%5C%22%3EMattress-in-a-box%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221380%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20mattress%20rolled%20up%20in%20plastic%20is%20displayed%20on%20piles%20of%20mattresses.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F665647ae239fda2da6cc63a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221035%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20mattress%20is%20condensed%20into%20a%20big%20log%20shape.%20Place%20on%20the%20bed%20before%20carefully%20removing%20the%20many%20plastic%20layers.%20I%20recommend%20using%20an%20envelope%20slitter.%3Cp%3EJames%20Brains%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat's%20the%20difference%20between%20a%20mattress%20in%20a%20box%20and%20a%20traditional%20mattress%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20line%20between%20the%20two%20continues%20to%20blur%2C%20a%20mattress%20in%20a%20box%20is%20traditionally%20made%20of%20foam%2C%20pocket%20coils%2C%20or%20a%20combination%20of%20the%20two%20and%20comes%20with%20a%20long%20home%20trial.%20Traditional%20mattresses%20feature%20innersprings%20that%20can't%20be%20compressed%20in%20a%20box.%20You%20can%20try%20them%20in%20showrooms%20before%20you%20buy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20long%20does%20a%20mattress%20in%20a%20box%20last%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20warranty%20is%20a%20good%20indicator%20of%20how%20long%20you%20can%20expect%20your%20mattress%20in%20a%20box%20to%20last.%20Most%20brands%20offer%20warranties%20of%20at%20least%2010%20years%2C%20so%20you%20can%20expect%20your%20mattress%20to%20last%20that%20long.%20Take%20advantage%20of%20the%20warranty%20if%20it%20shows%20significant%20defects%20or%20deterioration%20before%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20bed%20frames%20are%20suited%20for%20a%20mattress%20in%20a%20box%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20mattress%20brands%20will%20tell%20you%20what%20bed%20frames%20work%20best%20with%20the%20mattress%20you%20are%20buying.%20In%20general%2C%20you%20want%20a%20firm%2C%20supportive%20foundation.%20This%20might%20include%20wooden%20boards%20or%20slats%20that%20are%20no%20more%20than%20a%20couple%20of%20inches%20apart.%20Check%20out%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-bed-frame%5C%22%3Ebest%20bed%20frame%3C%2Fa%3E%20guide%20for%20the%20top%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20do%20you%20unbox%20a%20mattress%20in%20a%20box%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EUnbox%20your%20mattress%20within%20a%20day%20or%20two%20of%20its%20arrival%20since%20prolonged%20time%20spent%20in%20the%20vacuum%20seal%20could%20impact%20its%20structural%20integrity.%20With%20the%20help%20of%20another%20person%2C%20open%20one%20end%20of%20the%20box%20and%20tip%20it%20onto%20your%20foundation%20or%20one%20of%20our%20picks%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-bed-frame%5C%22%3Ebest%20bed%20frame%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Lift%20the%20unopened%20end%20of%20the%20box%20and%20shake%20the%20sealed%20mattress%20onto%20the%20foundation.%20Use%20extreme%20caution%20when%20removing%20the%20packaging%20and%20cut%20parallel%20to%20the%20mattress.%20You%20can%20use%20a%20slitter%20or%20other%20cutting%20implement%20to%20cut%20through%20the%20first%20layer%20of%20plastic%2C%20but%20it%20may%20be%20easier%20just%20to%20unroll%20the%20plastic%20with%20a%20yanking%20motion.%20Then%2C%20unfold%20the%20mattress%20onto%20your%20foundation.%20You%20may%20need%20to%20flip%20it%20so%20the%20top%20is%20facing%20up.%20Lastly%2C%20I%20use%20a%20yanking%20motion%20to%20keep%20the%20mattress%20in%20place%20to%20remove%20the%20plastic%20from%20the%20bottom%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20long%20does%20a%20mattress%20in%20a%20box%20take%20to%20expand%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20mattresses%20fully%20expand%20in%20a%20few%20hours%2C%20some%20can%20take%20up%20to%20three%20days.%20You%20can%20sleep%20on%20a%20mattress%20immediately%2C%20but%20I%20recommend%20letting%20it%20expand%20and%20off-gas.%20I%20unbox%20mattresses%20in%20the%20morning%3B%20by%20bedtime%2C%20they've%20usually%20fully%20expanded%2C%20and%20the%20new%20bed%20smell%20has%20disappeared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20long%20can%20a%20mattress%20stay%20in%20a%20box%20for%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMattresses%20can%20stay%20in%20a%20box%20for%20up%20to%20a%20month%20without%20experiencing%20damage.%20I%20recommend%20unboxing%20it%20at%20your%20earliest%20convenience%20because%20you%20don't%20know%20how%20long%20it's%20been%20in%20the%20box%20before%20arriving%20at%20your%20home.%20This%20will%20also%20give%20it%20time%20to%20air%20out.%20If%20you%20wait%20too%20long%20to%20open%20the%20mattress%2C%20it%20could%20void%20its%20warranty.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20happens%20to%20mattresses%20that%20are%20returned%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20varies%20by%20manufacturer.%20Once%20you%20sleep%20on%20a%20mattress%2C%20the%20manufacturer%20can't%20resell%20it.%20They%20may%20coordinate%20with%20a%20local%20organization%20to%20recycle%20your%20mattress%20or%20donate%20it.%20If%20you're%20concerned%20about%20the%20environmental%20impact%20your%20returned%20mattress%20might%20have%2C%20we%20encourage%20you%20to%20ask%20the%20manufacturer%20what%20they%20do%20with%20returned%20mattresses%20in%20your%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EAre%20beds%20in%20a%20box%20worth%20it%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EYes.%20Beds%20in%20a%20box%20are%20generally%20cheaper%20than%20traditional%20mattresses%2C%20yet%20they%20tend%20to%20be%20the%20same%20quality.%20While%20they%20aren't%20always%20available%20in%20showrooms%2C%20they%20come%20with%20a%20long%20trial%20period%2C%20so%20you%20can%20try%20them%20in%20a%20much%20better%20environment%3A%20your%20bedroom.%20Based%20on%20my%20experience%2C%20I'd%20choose%20a%20bed%20in%20a%20box%20when%20making%20a%20personal%20purchase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20overall%3A%20Leesa%20Sapira%20Hybrid%20Mattress%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20white%20quilted%20cover%20Leesa%20mattress%20is%20shown%20on%20gray%20bed%20frame%20with%20headboard%20and%20pillows.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63d2a54b40fbb600192b918a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Leesa%20Sapira%20is%20the%20best%20mattress%20in%20a%20box%20and%20is%20excellent%20for%20all%20sleeping%20positions.%3Cp%3ELeesa%3B%20Vicky%20Leta%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Caside%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBes