20company%20also%20follows%20sustainable%20practices%20in%20their%20production%20process.%20He%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20always%20been%20egar%20to%20be%20as%20sustainable%20in%20my%20lifestyle%20as%20possible.%20In%20an%20effort%20to%20do%20so%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20utilise%20the%20abundant%20sun%20to%20power%20my%20factory.%20Both%20of%20my%20factories%20in%20Nellore%20are%20powered%20by%20solar%20energy.%20It%20cost%20me%20about%20Rs%2045%20lakh.%20Currently%2C%20my%20factories%20run%20on%2080%20percent%20solar%20energy.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20wastewater%20generated%20from%20cleaning%20the%20machinery%20is%20recycled%20using%20an%20ETP%20plant%2C%20and%20the%20recycled%20water%20is%20utilised%20for%20gardening%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20various%20innovative%20flavours%20that%20the%20company%20makes%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9COur%20product%20range%20includes%20classic%20flavours%20like%20vanilla%2C%20butterscotch%2C%20and%20chocolate%2C%20as%20well%20as%20fruit%20flavours%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20pitaya%2C%20tender%20coconut%2C%20mango%2C%20chikoo%2C%20and%20jackfruit.%20We%20also%20offer%20innovative%20flavours%20like%20charcoal%2C%20which%20creates%20a%20striking%20black-coloured%20icecream.%20This%20unique%20flavour%20is%20a%20standout%20in%20our%20product%20lineup.%20We%20produce%20the%20charcoal%20by%20burning%20coconut%20shells%20and%20then%20using%20the%20resulting%20charcoal%20as%20an%20ingredient%20in%20our%20charcoal%20icecream.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20addition%20to%20our%20existing%20range%2C%20we%20have%20recently%20introduced%20a%20traditional%20milk%20category%20%E2%80%94%20featuring%20camel%20milk%20icecream%2C%20goat%20milk%20icecream%2C%20and%20donkey%20milk%20icecream.%20We%20are%20proud%20to%20be%20the%20first%20brand%20to%20offer%20these%20unique%20categories%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaheswaram%20Kumar%2C%20a%20regular%20customer%20says%2