to%20disclose%20this%20to%20his%20parents.%20In%20a%20stroke%20of%20resourcefulness%2C%20he%20secured%20a%20position%20at%20Ericsson%20India%20in%20Gurugram%20through%20a%20friend%2C%20earning%20Rs%209%2C000%20per%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20here%20in%20November%202014%20that%20the%20entrepreneur%20had%20his%20first%20bite%20of%20pizza%20with%20his%20friends%2C%20which%20changed%20his%20life%20forever.%20%E2%80%9CI%20loved%20the%20taste%20of%20the%20pizza%20and%20wondered%20how%20it%20was%20made.%20It%20seemed%20to%20be%20a%20fatter%20version%20of%20a%20%3Cem%3Eroti%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewith%20a%20different%20sauce%20and%20cheese%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sandeep%20recalls%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20few%20months%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20starting%20a%20food%20business%20crept%20into%20his%20mind.%20But%20how%20does%20one%20make%20a%20pizza%20and%20build%20a%20business%20around%20the%20same%3F%20To%20learn%20the%20nitty%20gritty%20of%20such%20a%20business%2C%20he%20approached%20a%20few%20pizza%20outlets%20in%20Gurugram%20and%20Haryana.%20It%20was%20Pizza%20Wings%20in%20Rohtak%20where%20he%20got%20a%20chance%20to%20learn%20the%20ABCs%20of%20running%20a%20pizza%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20trained%20for%20about%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%20at%20Pizza%20Wings.%20They%20taught%20me%20everything%20from%20how%20to%20make%20the%20dough%20and%20the%20sauce%20to%20how%20to%20deliver%20the%20pizza%20and%20run%20a%20store.%20I%20realised%20that%20making%20a%20pizza%20is%20not%20rocket%20science%2C%E2%80%9D%20laughs%20Sandeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20completing%20his%20training%2C%20Sandeep%20returned%20home%20and%20shared%20his%20ambitious%20business%20plan%20with%20his%20family%20%E2%80%94%20opening%20a%20pizza%20shop%20in%20the%20bustling%20city%20centre.%20However%2C%20his%20father%20was%20reluctant%20to%20invest%20in%20the%20venture.%20Undeterred%2C%20Sandeep%20sought%20sup