%20and%20huts.%20Those%20people%20were%20so%20proud%20of%20themselves%20that%20they%20never%20let%20me%20touch%20them.%20I%20was%20a%20distant%20admirer%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharda%20promised%20herself%20to%20create%20her%20own%20miniature%20gardens%20when%20her%20kids%20grow%20up.%20About%20three%20to%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20after%20her%20children%20left%20home%20for%20higher%20studies%20and%20jobs%2C%20she%20had%20all%20the%20time%20for%20herself.%20She%20missed%20her%20children%20and%20unleashed%20her%20thoughts%20and%20loneliness%20into%20creative%20tray%20gardens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20made%20a%20tray%20garden%20where%20I%20showed%20how%20my%20kids%20are%20now%20oceans%20apart%20from%20me.%20I%20missed%20their%20presence%2C%20especially%20during%20festivals.%20I%20also%20miss%20my%20life%20back%20in%20the%20village%2C%20how%20villagers%20celebrated%20festivals%20back%20then.%20Some%20people%20express%20their%20emotions%20through%20painting%20and%20poetry%2C%20I%20showcase%20it%20in%20my%20tray%20gardens%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20Republic%20Day%2C%20she%20created%20a%20miniature%20tray%20garden%20on%20the%20theme%2C%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3EJai%20Jawan%2C%20Jai%20Kisan%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20(Hail%20the%20Soldier%2C%20Hail%20the%20Farmer)%20in%20honour%20of%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20contribution%20to%20the%20nation.%20%E2%80%9CI%20designed%20tricolour%20in%20an%20oval-shaped%20tray%20and%20placed%20small%20grass%20and%20green%20plants%20on%20one%20side%20and%20white%20and%20saffron-coloured%20plants%20on%20the%20other.%20I%20also%20placed%20a%20small%20farmer.%20I%20was%20inspired%20to%20create%20this%20tray%20garden%20in%20honour%20of%20my%20father%2C%20who%20was%20a%20farmer%20and%20a%20freedom%20fighter%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fr