et%20of%20public%20toilets%20for%20women%20that%20stand%20in%20the%20Tukla%20and%20Urbis%20villages%20is%20the%20result%20of%20months%20of%20effort.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20villagers%20of%20Ladakh%20know%20her%20as%20the%20woman%20who%20has%20fought%20the%20authorities%20on%20their%20behalf%2C%20Upadhyaya%20says%20she%20is%20simply%20a%20changemaker.%20She%20calls%20herself%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F336971%2Fcourse-in-social-impact-for-changemakers-sp-jain-institute-post-graduate-programme-in-development-management%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esocial%20entrepreneur%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewho%20set%20out%20to%20reduce%20the%20chasm%20between%20Indian%20metropolitans%20and%20their%20rural%20counterparts%20%E2%80%94%20a%20feat%20that%20seemed%20impossible%20in%202014%20when%20she%20started.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20recalls%20another%20incident%20where%20she%20came%20face%20to%20face%20with%20the%20difficulties%20the%20locals%20of%20Ladakh%20faced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20shocked%20to%20learn%20that%20the%20villagers%20walked%2035%20km%20for%20a%20litre%20of%20oil.%20Imagine%20walking%20for%20five%20hours%20for%20a%20single%20litre!%E2%80%9D%20Appalled%2C%20she%20began%20approaching%20the%20authorities%20for%20an%20oil%20extraction%20machine%2C%20and%20within%20months%20the%20villagers%E2%80%99%20woes%20were%20eased.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20ask%20was%20delivered%2C%20their%20smiles%20were%20all%20the%20validation%20she%20looked%20for.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fguna-organics-1-1716442986.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20solar%20dryers%20are%20a%20step%20towards%20encouraging%20the%20farmers%20of%20Ladakh%