rky%20was%20designed%20by%20Maya%20and%20a%20team%20of%20students%20from%20The%20Progress%20High%20School%20in%20Panjim%2C%20Goa%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Maya%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELetting%20us%20in%20on%20her%20strategy%2C%20Usha%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20a%20few%20days%20to%20practise.%20I%20knew%20I%20had%20to%20make%20the%20most%20of%20them.%E2%80%9D%20She%20explains%20that%20the%20robot%20named%20%E2%80%98Quarky%E2%80%99%20was%20designed%20to%20perform%20tasks%20within%20a%20stipulated%20period%20of%20time.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20competition%20required%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340703%2Fkota-student-aryan-singh-invented-ai-powered-agrobot-runs-on-solar-energy%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20robot%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20perform%2011%20tasks%20within%20five%20minutes.%20So%2C%20I%20set%20aside%20two%20hours%20for%20practice%20every%20day%20and%20would%20put%20a%20timer%20on%20my%20father%E2%80%99s%20phone%20to%20measure%20how%20long%20I%20was%20taking%20for%20one%20task.%20Every%20day%20I%20would%20try%20to%20reduce%20this%20time.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2011%20challenges%2C%20she%20says%2C%20were%20designed%20to%20test%20the%20robot%E2%80%99s%20proficiency%20in%20matching%20colours%2C%20judging%20directions%2C%20navigating%20through%20a%20set%20of%20obstacles%2C%20segregating%20between%20items%2C%20and%20piecing%20together%20an%20order.%20And%20she%20delivered%20phenomenally!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20the%20moment%20her%20name%20was%20announced%20as%20the%20winner%2C%20Usha%20calls%20it%20surreal.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20made%20me%20very%20happy%20to%20see%20my%20parents%20and%20teachers%20feeling%20so%20proud.%20They%20did%20so%20much%20to%20bring%20me%20to%20this%20stage%20and%20winning%20felt%20amazing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20audience%20was%20cheering%20Usha%2C%20there%20was%20one%20person%20to%20whom%20the%20v